eely%20share%20his%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20full%20live%20performance%20as%20an%20avatar%20was%20always%20something%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20was%20excited%20about%20but%20couldn't%20wrap%20my%20head%20around%20how%20to%20execute%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Wave%20showed%20interest%20in%20teaming%20up%20for%20a%20concert%20series%2C%20it%20was%20a%20no-brainer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20market%20for%20immersive%20concerts%20and%20live%20experiences%20in%20VR%20will%20be%20a%20massive%20shift%20in%20the%20paradigm%20of%20performance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20artists%20and%20fans%20are%20interested%20in%20VR%20concerts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20appeal%20of%20VR%20concerts%20lies%20heavily%20in%20their%20experimental%20nature.%20Artists%20can%20try%20new%20ways%20to%20express%20themselves%20creatively%20and%20connect%20with%20listeners%20in%20digital%20environments.%20For%20fans%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faverage-ticket-cost-seatgeek-resale-doubled-over-5-years-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eskirting%20painful%20concert-ticket%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20avoiding%20large%20crowds%20at%20venues%2C%20and%20experiencing%20their%20favorite%20musicians%20in%20an%20alternate%20world%20are%20convincing%20perks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20one%20of%20the%20tech%20giants%20that%20has%20capitalized%20on%20these%20benefits.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20November%2C%20Meta%20Quest%20launched%20its%20Music%20Valley%20concert%20series.%20The%20ongoing%20series%20has%20featured%20virtual%20performances%20by%20artists%20such%20as%20Doja%20Cat%2C%20Blackpink%2C%20Victoria%20Mon%C3%A9t%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmusic-platforms-blockchain-artist-create-fan-clubs-communities-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJack%20Harlow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Jorja%20Smith.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarah%20Malkin%2C%20the%20director%20of%20metaverse%20entertainment%20content%20at%20Meta%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20virtual%20concerts%20served%20both%20creative%20and%20strategic%20purposes.%20%26quot%3BOften%20our%20VR%20shows%20are%20timed%20with%20key%20artist%20moments%20like%20tour%20launches%20or%20new%20music%20drops%2C%20helping%20performers%20reach%20their%20fans%20across%20multiple%20touchpoints%20and%20present%20their%20music%20or%20tour%20experiences%20in%20totally%20unique%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazeVR%2C%20an%20immersive-concert%20platform%20that%20launched%20in%202015%2C%20is%20another%20leader%20in%20the%20VR-entertainment%20space%20and%20has%20partnered%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20Sony%20Music%20and%20Roc%20Nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20its%20most%20notable%20collaborations%20was%20with%20Megan%20Thee%20Stallion%20%E2%80%94%20the%20star%20of%20AmazeVR's%20first%20VR-concert%20tour.%20Over%20three%20months%2C%20the%20artist's%20VR%20concert%20was%20available%20to%20watch%20at%20select%20theaters%20in%20different%20cities.%20Attendees%20who%20purchased%20tickets%20went%20to%20a%20designated%20theater%20where%20they%20were%20given%20VR%20headsets%20to%20view%20the%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteve%20Lee%2C%20the%20company's%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20debut%20tour%20was%20successful%2C%20with%20it%20selling%20out%20in%2015%20US%20cities%20and%20allowing%20consumers%20to%20%26quot%3Benjoy%20the%20magic%20of%20seeing%20their%20favorite%20artist%20in%20one%20of%20the%20most%20realistic%20forms%20%E2%80%94%20proving%20the%20power%20of%20VR.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20VR-concert%20tech%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20ways%20Meta%20captures%20VR%20concerts%20is%20by%20using%20purpose-built%20cameras%20to%20film%20artists%20at%20their%20real-life%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20determine%20the%20optimal%20placement%20of%20our%20specialized%20VR%20cameras%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20artists%20and%20their%20teams%2C%20integrating%20our%20capture%20system%20into%20their%20shows%20to%20provide%20the%20best%20possible%20viewing%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Malkin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20and%20the%20Diamond%20Bros%2C%20a%20creative-production%20company%2C%20used%20this%20approach%20to%20film%20a%20VR%20version%20of%20Doja%20Cat's%20sold-out%20Detroit%20show%20from%20her%20tour%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJason%20Diamond%2C%20the%20director%20and%20executive%20producer%20of%20the%20Diamond%20Bros%2C%20met%20with%20the%20artist's%20team%20to%20map%20out%20filming.%20They%20decided%20to%20use%20a%20stereoscopic%20technique%2C%20which%20employs%20a%20camera%20with%20two%20lenses%20that%20create%20a%203D%20effect.%20Diamond%20said%20the%20triangular%20stage%20was%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20for%20VR%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20allowed%20them%20to%20give%20a%20full%20view%20of%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20AmazeVR%2C%20Lee%20and%20his%20team%20are%20developing%20proprietary%20technologies%20to%20elevate%20VR%20music%20experiences.%20The%20company%20is%20using%20visual-effect%20modules%20and%20a%20custom%20renderer%20%E2%80%94%20used%20to%20generate%20an%20image%20from%20a%202D%20or%203D%20model%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepic-unreal-engine-apple-legal-battle-2020-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowered%20by%20artificial%20intelligence%20and%20Unreal%20Engine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20real-time%203D-creation%20tool.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20a%20top%20engineering%20team%2C%20the%20company's%20technologies%20allow%20it%20to%20capture%20immersive%20concert%20footage%20in%208K%20resolution%2C%20creating%20sharp%20visuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20technologies%20empower%20us%20to%20produce%20hyperrealistic%20VR%20concerts%20that%20make%20attendees%20feel%20as%20though%20they%20are%20face-to-face%20with%20the%20artists%2C%26quot%3B%20Lee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20downside%20of%20VR%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EVR%20has%20its%20kryptonite.%20Only%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farpost.co%2F2022%2F05%2F25%2Fnrg-report-vr-technology-consumer-attitudes%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Farpost.co%2F2022%2F05%2F25%2Fnrg-report-vr-technology-consumer-attitudes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E13%25%20of%20households%20in%20the%20US%20own%20a%20VR%20headset%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20the%20technology%20isn't%20ubiquitous.%20In%20a%20survey%20by%20Arris%20Composites%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farriscomposites.com%2Famericas-interest-in-virtual-and-augmented-reality%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E67%25%20of%20respondents%20who%20didn't%20own%20a%20VR%20headset%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcant-afford-apple-vision-pro-five-alternative-headsets-meta-quest-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehefty%20price%20tag%3C%2Fa%3E%20kept%20them%20from%20purchasing%20one%2C%20and%2033%25%20said%20they%20didn't%20think%20they%20would%20actually%20use%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20who%20paid%20a%20pretty%20penny%20for%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-vision-pro-returns-set-up-confusion-analyst-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20Vision%20Pro%20have%20returned%20the%20headset%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20they%20simply%20didn't%20know%20how%20to%20set%20it%20up%20or%20didn't%20think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-vision-pro-buyers-returning-headsets-design-blurry-screen-price-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20image%20quality%20was%20worth%20the%20cost%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiscomfort%20is%20another%20issue%3A%20Prolonged%20headset%20use%20could%20cause%20neck%20fatigue%20and%20eye%20strain%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fmedia%2F159709%2Fdownload%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAR%252FVR%2520devices%2520have%2520successfully%2Con%2520to%2520obtain%2520marketing%2520authorization.%26amp%3Btext%3DAs%2520part%2520of