C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuietist%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELevoit%20OasisMist%20450S%20Smart%20Humidifier%20-%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiipgf_062717_best-humidifiers-20%26h%3D79c9069064a583d289c12e6e2563855c34fded46fc1b3bb15cf2eb96aafd7829%26postID%3D61b8efc6f2a36b1ac9f4148b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-humidifier%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FLEVOIT-OasisMist-Humidifiers-Customized-Ultrasonic%252Fdp%252FB0B1DQ8KV3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESee%20at%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20overall%5C%22%3EBest%20overall%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Honeywell%20Designer%20Series%20Cool%20Mist%20Humidifier%20worked%20so%20quickly%20and%20efficiently%20on%20its%20highest%20setting%20in%20smaller%20bedrooms%20and%20offices%20that%20we%20worried%20about%20over-humidifying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20raised%20the%20humidity%20levels%20in%20our%20office%20by%2029%25%20in%20just%20four%20hours%2C%20a%20feat%20many%20of%20the%20other%20humidifiers%20we%20tested%20couldn't%20even%20accomplish%20after%20eight%20hours.%20Luckily%2C%20the%20settings%20are%20highly%20adjustable%20via%20an%20easy-to-use%20scroll%20knob%2C%20so%20you%20can%20set%20the%20humidifier%20to%20a%20lower%20level%20once%20your%20desired%20humidity%20has%20been%20reached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Honeywell%20is%20incredibly%20easy%20to%20use%3B%20setup%20took%20mere%20minutes.%20It%20has%20a%20simple%2C%20wide%20removable%20tank%20that%20you%20fill%20up%20and%20then%20slip%20back%20in.%20Plug%20it%20in%2C%20and%20you're%20ready%20to%20go.%20The%20humidifier%20also%20alerts%20you%20with%20a%20refill%20light%20when%20the%20water%20levels%20are%20low%20and%20automatically%20shuts%20off%20when%20empty.%20It%20can%20last%20a%20full%20day%20on%20one%20tank%20at%20the%20lowest%20settings.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20occasional%20dripping%20noise%2C%20though%20we%20didn't%20find%20it%20too%20distracting%2C%20and%20it's%20quiet%20enough%20that%20you%20won't%20hear%20it%20over%20a%20fan%20or%20some%20background%20music.%20While%20it%20worked%20well%20in%20smaller%20spaces%2C%20you%20may%20also%20want%20to%20use%20a%20fan%20near%20it%20for%20bigger%20rooms%20to%20help%20better%20disperse%20the%20vapor%20stream.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Honeywell%20humidifier%20has%20an%20essential%20oils%20feature%2C%20one%20pulmonologist%20we%20spoke%20to%20recommended%20against%20diffusing%20essential%20oils%20if%20you%20have%20respiratory%20issues.%20The%20American%20Academy%20of%20Allergy%2C%20Asthma%20%26amp%3B%20Immunology%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aaaai.org%2FAllergist-Resources%2FAsk-the-Expert%2FAnswers%2FOld-Ask-the-Experts%2Foil-diffusers-asthma%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20cautions%20against%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20humidifier%20is%20easy%20and%20quick%20to%20clean%20and%20doesn't%20require%20changing%20a%20filter.%20As%20a%20bonus%2C%20the%20sleek%20look%20is%20far%20more%20aesthetically%20pleasing%20than%20many%20other%20humidifiers%20on%20the%20market%2C%20and%20it%20can%20easily%20fit%20on%20most%20desks%2C%20nightstands%2C%20and%20shelves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20air%20purifying%5C%22%3EBest%20with%20air%20purifier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20getting%20around%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Dyson%20Purifier%20Humidify%2BCool%20is%20expensive.%20But%20as%20a%20three-in-one%20machine%20that's%20also%20an%20air%20purifier%20and%20a%20fan%2C%20you%20can%20make%20the%20case%20that%20it's%20more%20convenient%20and%20potentially%20cheaper%20just%20to%20get%20the%20Dyson%20rather%20than%20buy%20those%20three%20devices%20separately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Dyson%20has%20a%20smaller%20footprint%20than%20the%20three%20machines%20would%20separately%2C%20it%20will%20take%20up%20some%20floor%20space.%20That%20said%2C%20for%20those%20in%20the%20market%20for%20a%20smart%20humidifier%20and%20air%20purifier%20option%20that%20does%20all%20the%20thinking%20for%20you%2C%20the%20Dyson%20Purifier%20Humidify%2BCool%20is%20an%20excellent%20choice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20connect%20the%20Dyson%20to%20the%20MyDyson%20app%20(available%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fdyson-link%2Fid993135524%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.dyson.mobile.android%26hl%3Den_US%26gl%3DUS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndroid%3C%2Fa%3E)%20to%20check%20your%20current%20home%20humidity%20and%20air%20quality%20levels.%20The%20machine%20can%20be%20controlled%20with%20a%20remote%2C%20the%20app%2C%20and%20via%20voice%20control%20with%20Alexa%20and%20Siri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20you%20can%20change%20the%20humidity%20and%20fan%20levels%20yourself%2C%20you%20can%20also%20set%20it%20to%20auto%2C%20and%20it%20will%20decide%20the%20best%20levels%20for%20you%20based%20on%20local%20weather%20data%20and%20your%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20score.%20When%20we%20used%20the%20auto%20feature%2C%20it%20raised%20humidity%20levels%20to%20a%20nice%2050%25%20and%20kept%20it%20there%20even%20throughout%20a%20larger%20open-concept%20kitchen%20and%20living%20room%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%201-gallon%20tank%20also%20lasts%20a%20long%20time.%20Dyson%20claims%20it%20lasts%20for%2036%20hours%20even%20on%20high%20settings%2C%20and%20though%20we%20didn't%20time%20it%20down%20to%20the%20exact%20hour%2C%20one%20tank%20could%20easily%20last%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20it's%20also%20a%20fan%20makes%20this%20a%20nice%20year-round%20option%2C%20as%20it%20can%20easily%20switch%20between%20adding%20extra%20humidity%20during%20winter%20months%20to%20circulating%20cool%20air%20on%20sticky%20summer%20nights.%20While%20the%20fan%20is%20very%20loud%20on%20its%20highest%20settings%2C%20it's%20nice%20and%20quiet%20on%20settings%20of%204%20and%20under%2C%20and%20it%20does%20have%20a%20night-mode%20feature%20that%20will%20keep%20everything%20automatic%20but%20at%20the%20quietest%20levels%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20for%20anyone%20who%20worries%20about%20potential%20bacteria%20from%20humidifiers%2C%20the%20Dyson%20uses%20UV%20light%20to%20kill%20bacteria%20before%20expelling%20the%20(invisible)%20water%20vapor%20into%20the%20air.%20It%20alerts%20you%20when%20it%20needs%20cleaning%20and%20comes%20with%20citrus%20powder%20packets%20for%20that%20purpose%20(you%20can%20also%20buy%20your%20own).%20Fill%20the%20water%20tank%2C%20add%20a%20packet%2C%20and%20hit%20the%20self-clean%20button.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20haven't%20needed%20to%20change%20the%20HEPA%20filter%20yet%2C%20but%20be%20aware%20those%20will%20cost%20you%20an%20additional%20%2480%20every%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20bedrooms%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20bedrooms%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Levoit%20Classic%20300S%20Humidifier%20runs%20as%20quiet%20as%20ambient%20noise%2C%20has%20a%20small%20footprint%2C%20and%20features%20a%20nightlight%2C%20making%20it%20ideal%20for%20the%20bedroom%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-humidifier-for-baby%5C%22%3Ebest%20humidifier%20for%20your%20baby%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Don't%20want%20a%20nightlight%3F%20No%20problem.%20You%20can%20turn%20off%20the%20display%20to%20achieve%20darkness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Levoit%20Classic%20300S%20Humidifier%20did%20an%20excellent%20job%20of%20humidifying%20a%20100-square-foot%20office%20during%20testing.%20On%20a%20particularly%20dry%20winter%20day%2C%20it%20steadily%20increased%20the%20office%20humidity%20by%2011%25%20in%20four%20hours.%20We%20let%20it%20run%20overnight%2C%20and%20the%20humidity%20increased%20by%20another%2011%25%20by%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20button%20controls%20on%20the%20unit%20are%20intuitive%2C%20we%20especially%20like%20that%20you%20can%20monitor%20and%20adjust%20the%20300S%20using%20the%20VeSync%20app%20(available%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fvesync%2Fid1289575311%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.etekcity.vesyncplatform%26hl%3Den_US%26gl%3DUS%26pli%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndroid%3C%2Fa%3E.)%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20app%20sends%20a%20push%20notification%20when%20the%20tank%20needs%20refilling%20or%20cleaning.%20In%20tests%2C%20the%20humidifier%20ran%20on%20top%20mist%20level%20for%2024%20hours%20before%20needing%20a%20refill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20operate%20the%20Levoit%20Classic%20300S%20in%20manual%20or%20auto%20mode.%20We%20preferred%20manual%20mode%20because%20the%20built-in%20hygrometer%20showed%20higher%20readings%20than%20the%20hygrometer%20we%20placed%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20room.%20Thus%2C%20it%20would%20shut%20off%20before%20areas%20further%20from%20the%20unit%20were%20at%20the%20desired%20humidity%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECleaning%20the%20humidifier%20was%20relatively%20easy%20using%20the%20in-app%20step-by-step%20instructions%20and%20an%20included%20brush.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20travel%5C%22%3EBest%20travel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20humidifiers%20have%20less%20range%20than%20their%20larger%20counterparts%2C%20but%20their%20smaller%20size%20makes%20them%20easy%20to%20bring%20on%20the%20go%20or%20to%20move%20throughout%20your%20home%20as%20needed.%20The%20Hey%20Dewy%20humidifier%20stands%20out%20among%20travel%20humidifiers%20for%20its%20larger%2011.3-ounce%20tank%20size%2C%20powerful%20mist%2C%20and%20long-lasting%20charge.%20It%20didn't%20pump%20up%20the%20overall%20room%20humidity%20quite%20as%20much%20as%20the%20traditional%20humidifiers%20we%20tested%2C%20but%20it%20still%20helped%20add%20plenty%20of%20moisture%20to%20the%20room%2C%20especially%20at%20close%20range.%20After%20seven%20hours%2C%20it%20raised%20the%20humidity%20by%206%25%20in%20a%20four-foot%20range%20and%2013%25%20in%20a%20two-foot%20range.%20So%2C%20it%20may%20be%20a%20good%20option%20to%20set%20your%20humidifier%20on%20your%20desk%20or%20park%20it%20next%20to%20your%20indoor%20plants.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20humidifier%20doesn't%20make%20much%20noise%2C%20you%20can%20hear%20it%20running%20from%20across%20the%20room.%20When%20set%20to%20the%20continuous%20mist%20option%2C%20the%20sound%20worked%20well%20as%20gentle%20white%20noise%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20on-off%20sound%20of%20the%20intermittent%20spray%20could%20be%20distracting%20at%20bedtime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20humidifier's%20filter%20needs%20to%20be%20replaced%20at%20least%20every%20six%20months.%20However%2C%20this%20may%20not%20necessarily%20be%20a%20drawback%20since%20the%20filter%20means%20you%20can%20use%20tap%20water%20instead%20of%20distilled%20water.%20The%20unit%20comes%20pre-assembled%20with%20the%20filter%20in%20place%2C%20and%20once%20charged%2C%20it%20will%20run%20wirelessly%20for%20about%20eight%20hours.%20However%2C%20the%20water%20may%20run%20out%20before%20the%20unit%20needs%20recharging.%20In%20testing%2C%20we%20found%20that%20a%20full%20tank%20of%20water%20only%20lasted%20about%20six%20hours%20with%20a%20continuous%20mist%20spray.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20quiet%5C%22%3EQuietist%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20first%20turn%20the%20Levoit%20OasisMist%20450S%20Smart%20Humidifier%20on%2C%20you'll%20hear%20some%20trickling%20%E2%80%94%20but%20once%20it%20gets%20going%2C%20you%20won't%20hear%20much.%20This%20humidifier%20remains%20extremely%20quiet%20on%20all%20cool%20mist%20settings%2C%20though%20it%20gets%20slightly%20louder%20when%20producing%20warm%20mist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20quiet%20operation%2C%20this%20machine%20humidifies%20rooms%20very%20efficiently%2C%20with%20no%20noticeable%20condensation%20leakage.%20Two%20nozzles%20rotate%20360%20degrees%20so%20you%20can%20aim%20both%20mist%20plumes%20in%20any%20direction.%20We%20tested%20it%20in%20a%20room%20of%20roughly%20230%20square%20feet%2C%20and%20the%20humidity%20shot%20up%20by%208%25%20within%20just%20one%20hour.%20If%20your%20room%20is%20any%20smaller%20than%20215%20square%20feet%20%E2%80%94%20the%20brand's%20recommended%20lower%20range%20%E2%80%94%20this%20option%20may%20end%20up%20over-humidifying%20your%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20like%20smart%20features%2C%20this%20humidifier%20comes%20well-equipped.%20It's%20compatible%20with%20Amazon%20Alexa%20and%20Google%20Voice%2C%20and%20you%20can%20use%20the%20free%20VeSync%20app%20to%20control%20the%20humidifier's%20settings%2C%20check%20the%20humidity%20in%20the%20room%2C%20set%20it%20to%20auto%20mode%2C%20or%20schedule%20shutoff.%20The%20humidifier%20will%20also%20shut%20down%20automatically%20once%20the%20tank%20empties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20tank%20means%20this%20humidifier%20takes%20up%20more%20space%20in%20your%20room.%20But%20that%20could%20be%20a%20plus%20since%20a%20bigger%20tank%20means%20it%20can%20run%20for%20longer%20between%20refills%3A%20After%2024%20hours%20of%20testing%20on%20medium%20and%20high%20operation%2C%20some%20water%20remained%20in%20the%20tank.%20If%20you%20keep%20the%20humidifier%20on%20low%2C%20it%20can%20run%20for%20up%20to%2045%20hours.%20Another%20bonus%20of%20the%20large%20tank%20is%20a%20smoother%20cleaning%20process.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20entire%20top%20of%20the%20tank%20comes%20off%2C%20making%20it%20very%20easy%20to%20scrub.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20humidifier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20a%20humidifier%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20consider%20important%20features%20like%20your%20room%20size%2C%20whether%20you%20want%20a%20filter%2C%20and%20mist%20temperature.%20Here%20are%20some%20more%20details%20to%20guide%20your%20shopping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoom%20size%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20first%20step%20you%20should%20always%20take%20is%20knowing%20the%20room's%20square%20footage%20you%20want%20to%20humidify.%20You%20can%20measure%20your%20room's%20square%20footage%20with%20a%20tape%20measure.%20Then%2C%20read%20up%20on%20the%20humidifier%20you're%20considering%20and%20whether%20the%20brand%20recommends%20it%20for%20small%2C%20medium%2C%20or%20large%20spaces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20buy%20a%20model%20that%20is%20designed%20for%20a%20larger%20space%2C%20the%20room%20will%20be%20uncomfortably%20humid%20and%20create%20an%20environment%20that%20could%20encourage%20mold%20and%20mildew%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sydney%20Rexroad%2C%20communications%20associate%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aham.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssociation%20of%20Home%20Appliance%20Manufacturers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20model%20is%20too%20small%2C%20it%20won't%20generate%20adequate%20humidity%20for%20the%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFilter%20versus%20filter-free%20models%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYour%20choice%20here%20may%20depend%20on%20a%20few%20factors%20since%20one%20isn't%20necessarily%20better.%20%26quot%3BFiltered%20humidifiers%20are%20evaporative%20and%20use%20a%20fan%20to%20humidify%20the%20air.%20Filter-free%20models%20will%20put%20a%20mist%20directly%20into%20the%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20Rexroad%20says.%20Additionally%2C%20filter-free%20models%20have%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20bacteria%20or%20allergens%20getting%20into%20the%20air%2C%20so%20be%20sure%20you%20can%20clean%20it%20thoroughly%20at%20least%20once%20a%20week.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20filters%20need%20to%20be%20replaced%2C%20which%20adds%20cost%20you%20may%20not%20want%20to%20take%20on.%20Filter%20models%20are%20often%20noisier%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECold%20mist%20versus%20warm%20mist%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAccording%20to%20all%20three%20experts%20we%20spoke%20with%2C%20this%20is%20entirely%20based%20on%20personal%20preference.%20Depending%20on%20your%20main%20use%20for%20the%20humidifier%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20ask%20your%20healthcare%20provider%20before%20making%20a%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmall%20versus%20large%20humidifiers%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGenerally%20speaking%2C%20larger%20humidifiers%20have%20bigger%20tanks%2C%20meaning%20they%20can%20run%20longer%20between%20refills.%20Smaller%20humidifiers%20are%20easier%20to%20move%20throughout%20your%20house%20or%20take%20with%20you%20when%20you%20travel%2C%20but%20some%20may%20not%20last%20an%20entire%20day%20or%20night%20when%20set%20to%20high.%20That%20said%2C%20if%20the%20room%20you%20want%20to%20humidify%20is%20on%20the%20smaller%20side%2C%20a%20larger%20humidifier%20may%20add%20too%20much%20moisture%20to%20the%20air.%20According%20to%20the%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency%20(EPA)%2C%20indoor%20humidity%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Fmold%2Fmold-course-chapter-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshould%20never%20rise%20about%2060%25%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20because%20too-high%20humidity%20can%20lead%20to%20mold%20growth.%20You%20can%20check%20the%20humidity%20in%20your%20room%20with%20a%20hygrometer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdditional%20features%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHumidifiers%20have%20one%20main%20function%3A%20adding%20moisture%20to%20the%20air.%20If%20you%20want%20a%20humidifier%20that%20performs%20more%20than%20one%20service%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20look%20for%20a%20model%20that%20states%20it%20was%20made%20to%20do%20so.%20We%20recommend%20avoiding%20diffusing%20essential%20oils%2C%20but%20if%20you%20choose%20to%20do%20so%2C%20pick%20a%20model%20explicitly%20for%20that%20dual%20purpose.%20For%20example%2C%20some%20humidifiers%20have%20essential%20oil%20trays%20beneath%20the%20tank%20where%20you%20can%20add%20a%20drop%20or%20two%20of%20your%20chosen%20oil.%20Never%20put%20the%20oil%20directly%20into%20the%20machine.%20%26quot%3BEssential%20oils%2C%20medications%2C%20or%20other%20substances%20can%20damage%20the%20humidifier's%20mechanical%20parts%2C%26quot%3B%20Rexroad%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20humidifiers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%2010%20popular%20humidifiers%20for%20this%20guide.%20What%20you%20need%20from%20a%20humidifier%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20size%20of%20your%20space%2C%20how%20frequently%20you%20want%20to%20use%20it%2C%20and%20your%20main%20goal%20for%20humidifying.%20However%2C%20some%20universal%20factors%20make%20for%20a%20good%20humidifier.%20Here's%20what%20we%20looked%20for%20while%20testing%20and%20choosing%20our%20top%20picks%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHumidity%20increase%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20is%20the%20most%20obvious%20and%20most%20important%20factor.%20If%20a%20humidifier%20doesn't%20raise%20the%20humidity%20levels%20of%20your%20space%20to%20the%20EPA-recommended%2030%25%20to%2050%25%2C%20it%20doesn't%20serve%20its%20main%20function.%20We%20used%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbuythermopro.com%2Fproduct%2Fthermopro-tp-50-temperature-and-humidity-monitor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehygrometer%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20definitively%20test%20the%20humidity%20levels%20of%20our%20space%20before%2C%20during%2C%20and%20after%20using%20each%20humidifier.%20We%20tested%20the%20levels%20right%20near%20the%20humidifiers%20and%20across%20rooms%20of%20various%20sizes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20setup%20and%20use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20a%20humidifier%20is%20hard%20to%20figure%20out%2C%20a%20pain%20to%20fill%20up%2C%20or%20doesn't%20last%20a%20full%20day%20or%20night%20on%20one%20tank%20fill%2C%20chances%20are%20you%20won't%20want%20to%20use%20it%20very%20often.%20Our%20top%20picks%20take%20five%20minutes%20or%20less%20to%20set%20up%2C%20are%20easy%20to%20fill%2C%20and%20last%20at%20least%2010%20hours%20on%20one%20tank.%20Some%20can%20even%20last%20days%20on%20a%20single%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20cleaning%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Without%20proper%20cleaning%2C%20humidifiers%20can%20grow%20mold%20or%20bacteria%20that%20can%20then%20be%20dispersed%20into%20your%20home.%20We%20did%20a%20deep%20clean%20of%20every%20humidifier%20we%20chose%20and%20found%20it%20to%20be%20an%20easy%20process%20for%20all%20of%20our%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExtra%20features%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Some%20humidifiers%20come%20with%20fancy%20extras%20that%20range%20from%20simple%20night-light%20settings%20to%20app%20and%20voice%20control.%20These%20extras%20were%20considered%20to%20discern%20if%20they%20provided%20additional%20value%20and%20ease%20of%20use.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELongevity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We've%20tested%20most%20of%20these%20humidifiers%20for%20about%20two%20months%20and%20have%20not%20encountered%20issues%20with%20the%20top%20choices.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20test%20to%20ensure%20they%20hold%20up%20over%20time%20and%20no%20serious%20problems%20arise%2C%20such%20as%20mold%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EHumidifier%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20humidifiers%20good%20for%20the%20lungs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Purvi%20Parikh%2C%20an%20adult%20and%20pediatric%20allergist%20and%20immunologist%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fallergyasthmanetwork.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAllergy%20%26amp%3B%20Asthma%20Network%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20dry%20air%20can%20worsen%20allergy%20and%20asthma%20symptoms.%20Introducing%20a%20humidifier%20will%20moisten%20the%20air%2C%20which%20may%20help%20protect%20your%20lungs%20from%20irritants.%20However%2C%20keeping%20the%20humidifier%20clean%20is%20essential%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Findoor-air-quality-iaq%2Fuse-and-care-home-humidifiers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevent%20mold%20and%20bacteria%20buildup%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Additionally%2C%20only%20use%20distilled%20water%20in%20your%20humidifier%20unless%20the%20device%20specifically%20says%20to%20use%20tap%20water.%20Tap%20water%20can%20release%20minerals%20into%20the%20air%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mcgill.ca%2Foss%2Farticle%2Fcritical-thinking-health%2Fquestions-abound-safety-humidifiers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperts%3C%2Fa%3E%20don't%20yet%20know%20the%20long-term%20health%20effects%20of%20breathing%20in%20these%20particles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20a%20cool%20mist%20or%20warm%20mist%20humidifier%20better%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWarm%20and%20cool%20mist%20humidifiers%20work%20equally%20well%20to%20add%20moisture%20to%20the%20air%2C%20so%20Rexroad%20and%20Parikh%20suggest%20letting%20your%20personal%20preferences%20guide%20you%20in%20this%20decision.%20If%20a%20doctor%20or%20other%20healthcare%20professional%20recommends%20using%20a%20humidifier%2C%20check%20with%20them%20to%20find%20out%20if%20a%20cool%20mist%20or%20warm%20mist%20would%20help%20you%20get%20the%20most%20relief.%20You%20may%20also%20prefer%20a%20warm%20mist%20humidifier%20during%20the%20colder%20months.%20Remember%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinic.org%2Fdiseases-conditions%2Fcommon-cold%2Fexpert-answers%2Fcool-mist-humidifiers%2Ffaq-20058199%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Mayo%20Clinic%20warns%20against%20using%20warm-mist%20humidifiers%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20babies%20and%20children%20since%20they%20pose%20a%20risk%20of%20burns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20most%20effective%20type%20of%20humidifier%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20effective%20humidifier%20should%20raise%20the%20humidity%20in%20a%20room%20without%20over-humidifying.%20Our%20picks%20raised%20room%20humidity%20by%20at%20least%206%25%20over%20eight%20hours.%20However%2C%20since%20experts%20recommend%20keeping%20the%20humidity%20level%20in%20your%20home%20between%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinic.org%2Fdiseases-conditions%2Fcommon-cold%2Fin-depth%2Fhumidifiers%2Fart-20048021%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%25%20and%2050%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20most%20effective%20humidifier%20for%20you%20will%20help%20maintain%20this%20humidity%20level.%20If%20you'd%20like%20to%20use%20your%20humidifier%20to%20help%20ease%20congestion%2C%20dry%20skin%2C%20and%20other%20symptoms%2C%20a%20healthcare%20professional%20can%20provide%20more%20guidance%20on%20choosing%20a%20humidifier%20for%20your%20specific%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20humidifiers%20are%20best%20for%20winter%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20humidifier%20during%20the%20winter%20can%20be%20helpful%20because%20indoor%20heating%20can%20cause%20the%20air%20to%20dry%20out%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flunginstitute.com%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristine%20Kingsley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20advanced%20practice%20registered%20nurse%20and%20the%20Health%20and%20Wellness%20Director%20of%20the%20Lung%20Institute.%20%26quot%3BHumidifiers%20add%20moisture%20to%20the%20air%2C%20alleviating%20symptoms%20of%20dry%20skin%2C%20dry%20throat%2C%20and%20sinus%20congestion%2C%26quot%3B%20Kingsley%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20prefer%20warm-mist%20humidifiers%20during%20the%20colder%20months.%20These%20humidifiers%20disperse%20vapor%20by%20heating%20water%2C%20adding%20warmth%20to%20chilly%20rooms.%20But%20Kingsley%20cautions%20that%20warm%20mist%20can%20create%20an%20extremely%20humid%20environment%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20mold%20and%20bacteria%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20I%20need%20an%20air%20purifier%20and%20humidifier%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fshould-you-buy-all-in-one-humidifier-air-purifier%5C%22%3Eair%20purifier%3C%2Fa%3E%20removes%20pollutants%2C%20helping%20reduce%20potentially%20irritating%20particles%20like%20dust%2C%20pollen%2C%20and%20pet%20dander%2C%20says%20John%20Landry%2C%20licensed%20registered%20respiratory%20therapist%20and%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.respiratorytherapyzone.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERespiratory%20Therapy%20Zone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Landry%20says%20a%20humidifier%20adds%20moisture%20to%20the%20air%2C%20which%20can%20help%20soothe%20dry%20skin%2C%20sinus%20congestion%2C%20and%20respiratory%20issues.%20You%20may%20benefit%20from%20an%20air%20purifier%20if%20you%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F29549698%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseasonal%20allergies%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F29549698%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easthma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20a%20humidifier%20may%20offer%20relief%20if%20you%20live%20in%20a%20drier%20climate%20or%20have%20dry%20skin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20humidifiers%20are%20safe%20for%20children%20and%20babies%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Academy%20of%20Pediatrics%20considers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthychildren.org%2FEnglish%2Fsafety-prevention%2Fat-home%2FPages%2FMake-Babys-Room-Safe.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecool%20mist%20humidifiers%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20safest%20option%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-humidifier-for-baby%5C%22%3Ebabies%20and%20young%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Warm%20mist%20humidifiers%20work%20by%20producing%20steam%2C%20which%20can%20be%20hot%20enough%20to%20burn%20a%20curious%20toddler%20who%20tries%20to%20touch%20it.%20Whichever%20type%20of%20humidifier%20you%20choose%2C%20always%20set%20it%20somewhere%20out%20of%20reach%20of%20children%20and%20pets.%20Another%20important%20part%20of%20humidifier%20safety%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.childrenscolorado.org%2Fconditions-and-advice%2Fparenting%2Fparenting-articles%2Fdanger-of-humidifiers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20using%20distilled%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20free%20of%20minerals%20that%20may%20evaporate%20into%20your%20household%20air%2C%20and%20cleaning%20the%20unit%20regularly%20with%20vinegar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20often%20do%20you%20need%20to%20clean%20a%20humidifier%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EPA%20advises%20cleaning%20your%20humidifier%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Findoor-air-quality-iaq%2Fuse-and-care-home-humidifiers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevery%20third%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%203%25%20hydrogen%20peroxide%20solution.%20You%20can%20also%20clean%20your%20humidifier%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.childrenscolorado.org%2Fconditions-and-advice%2Fparenting%2Fparenting-articles%2Fdanger-of-humidifiers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evinegar%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20clean%20your%20humidifier%20properly%2C%20unplug%20the%20unit%20and%20then%20use%20a%20scrubbing%20brush%20to%20clean%20all%20surfaces%20that%20touch%20water.%20If%20you%20use%20any%20chemicals%20to%20clean%20your%20humidifier%2C%20take%20care%20to%20rinse%20it%20several%20times%20with%20clean%20tap%20water%20before%20using%20it%20again.%20You%20can%20check%20the%20instruction%20booklet%20that%20came%20with%20your%20humidifier%20for%20additional%20cleaning%20instructions%20specific%20to%20your%20unit.%20If%20you%20don't%20intend%20to%20use%20your%20humidifier%20for%20a%20while%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20clean%20it%20out%20and%20allow%20it%20to%20fully%20dry%20before%20you%20store%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20humidifier%20overall%3A%20Honeywell%20Designer%20Series%20Cool%20Mist%20Humidifier%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Honeywell%20Designer%20Series%20Cool%20Mist%20Humidifier%20HUL430%2C%20the%20best%20humidifier%20in%202022%2C%20is%20displayed%20next%20to%20a%20sofa.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F639b34a127c0a700193e4358%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETarget%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaised%20humidity%20level%20by%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2029%25%20in%204%20hours%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERun%20time%20between%20refills%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2024%20hours%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDimensions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%208.8%20x%208.8%20x%2013.2%20inches%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EColor%20options%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20White%2C%20black%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Adjustable%20settings%2C%20extremely%20efficient%2C%20easy%20to%20set%20up%20and%20clean%2C%20lasts%2024%20hours%20on%20one%20tank%2C%20no%20filter%20to%20change%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Occasional%20dripping%20noise%2C%20no%20smart%20settings%2C%20doesn't%20disperse%20humidity%20as%20evenly%20in%20large%20rooms%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Honeywell%20Designer%20Series%20Cool%20Mist%20Humidifier%20worked%20so%20quickly%20and%20efficiently%20on%20its%20highest%20setting%20in%20a%20smaller%20bedroom%20and%20office%20spaces%20that%20we%20actually%20worried%20about%20over-humidifying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20it%20raised%20the%20humidity%20levels%20in%20our%20office%20by%2029%25%20in%20just%20four%20hours%2C%20a%20feat%20many%20of%20the%20other%20humidifiers%20we%20tested%20couldn't%20even%20accomplish%20after%20eight%20hours.%20Luckily%2C%20the%20settings%20are%20highly%20adjustable%20via%20an%20easy-to-use%20scroll%20knob%20so%20you%20can%20set%20the%20humidifier%20to%20a%20lower%20level%20once%20your%20desired%20humidity%20has%20been%20reached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Honeywell%20is%20incredibly%20easy%20to%20use%3B%20setup%20took%20mere%20minutes.%20It%20has%20a%20simple%2C%20wide%20removable%20tank%20that%20you%20fill%20up%20and%20then%20slip%20back%20in.%20Plug%20it%20in%2C%20and%20you're%20ready%20to%20go.%20The%20humidifier%20also%20alerts%20you%20with%20a%20refill%20light%20when%20the%20water%20levels%20are%20low%2C%20and%20it%20automatically%20shuts%20off%20when%20it's%20empty.%20On%20the%20lowest%20settings%2C%20it%20can%20last%20for%20a%20full%20day%20on%20one%20tank.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20occasional%20dripping%20noise%2C%20though%20we%20didn't%20find%20it%20too%20distracting%2C%20and%20it's%20quiet%20enough%20that%20you%20won't%20hear%20it%20over%20a%20fan%20or%20some%20background%20music.%20While%20it%20worked%20more%20than%20well%20enough%20on%20its%20own%20in%20smaller%20spaces%2C%20you%20may%20also%20want%20to%20use%20a%20fan%20near%20it%20for%20bigger%20rooms%20to%20help%20better%20disperse%20the%20vapor%20stream.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Honeywell%20humidifier%20has%20an%20essential%20oils%20feature%2C%20one%20pulmonologist%20we%20spoke%20to%20recommended%20against%20diffusing%20essential%20oils.%20The%20American%20Academy%20of%20Allergy%2C%20Asthma%20%26amp%3B%20Immunology%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aaaai.org%2FAllergist-Resources%2FAsk-the-Expert%2FAnswers%2FOld-Ask-the-Experts%2Foil-diffusers-asthma%5C%22%3Ealso%20cautions%20against%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20filter%20that%20needs%20changing%2C%20and%20it's%20easy%20and%20quick%20to%20clean.%20As%20a%20bonus%2C%20its%20sleek%20look%20is%20far%20more%20aesthetically%20pleasing%20than%20many%20other%20humidifiers%20on%20the%20market%2C%20and%20it%20can%20easily%20fit%20on%20most%20desks%2C%20nightstands%2C%20and%20shelves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20humidifier%20air%20purifier%3A%20Dyson%20Pure%20Humidify%20%2B%20Cool%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Dyson%20Pure%20Humidify%20%2B%20Cool%2C%20the%20best%20humidifier%20air%20purifier%20in%202022%2C%20is%20displayed%20in%20a%20bedroom%20at%20night.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F639b34a2b7e0f20018092a0c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBest%20Buy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaised%20humidity%20level%20by%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%206%25%20in%204%20hours%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERun%20time%20between%20refills%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2036%2B%20hours%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDimensions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2036.5%20x%2011%20x%206%20inches%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EColor%20options%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20White%2Fsilver%2C%20black%2Fnickel%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Smart%20automatic%20features%2C%20works%20with%20an%20app%2C%20reads%20home%20and%20outside%20air%20levels%2C%20easy%20cleaning%20mode%2C%20three-in-one%20machine%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Takes%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20space%2C%20very%20expensive%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20getting%20around%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Dyson%20Pure%20Humidify%20%2B%20Cool%20is%20expensive.%20But%20as%20a%20three-in-one%20machine%20that's%20also%20an%20air%20purifier%20and%20a%20fan%2C%20you%20can%20make%20the%20case%20that%20it's%20more%20convenient%20and%20potentially%20cheaper%20just%20to%20get%20the%20Dyson%20rather%20than%20buy%20those%20three%20devices%20separately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Dyson%20has%20a%20smaller%20footprint%20than%20three%20machines%20would%20separately%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20take%20up%20some%20floor%20space.%20That%20said%2C%20for%20those%20in%20the%20market%20for%20a%20smart%20humidifier%20and%20air%20purifier%20option%20that%20does%20all%20the%20thinking%20for%20you%2C%20the%20Dyson%20Pure%20Humidify%20%2B%20Cool%20is%20an%20excellent%20choice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20connect%20the%20Dyson%20to%20the%20MyDyson%20app%20(available%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fdyson-link%2Fid993135524%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.dyson.mobile.android%26hl%3Den_US%26gl%3DUS%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndroid%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20and%20from%20there%20you%20can%20check%20your%20current%20home%20humidity%20and%20air%20quality%20levels.%20The%20machine%20can%20be%20controlled%20with%20a%20remote%2C%20the%20app%2C%20and%20via%20voice%20control%20with%20Alexa%20and%20Siri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20you%20can%20change%20the%20humidity%20and%20fan%20levels%20yourself%2C%20you%20can%20also%20set%20it%20to%20auto%2C%20and%20it%20will%20decide%20the%20best%20levels%20for%20you%20based%20on%20local%20weather%20data%20and%20your%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20score.%20When%20we%20used%20the%20auto%20feature%2C%20it%20raised%20humidity%20levels%20to%20a%20nice%2050%25%20and%20kept%20it%20there%20even%20throughout%20a%20larger%20open-concept%20kitchen%20and%20living%20room%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%201-gallon%20tank%20also%20lasts%20a%20long%20time.%20Dyson%20claims%20it%20lasts%20for%2036%20hours%20even%20on%20high%20settings%2C%20and%20though%20we%20didn't%20time%20it%20down%20to%20the%20exact%20hour%2C%20one%20tank%20was%20easily%20able%20to%20last%20a%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20it's%20also%20a%20fan%20makes%20this%20a%20nice%20year-round%20option%2C%20as%20it%20can%20easily%20switch%20between%20adding%20extra%20humidity%20during%20winter%20months%20to%20circulating%20cool%20air%20on%20sticky%20summer%20nights.%20While%20the%20fan%20is%20very%20loud%20on%20its%20highest%20settings%2C%20it's%20nice%20and%20quiet%20on%20settings%20of%204%20and%20under%2C%20and%20it%20does%20have%20a%20night-mode%20feature%20that%20will%20keep%20everything%20automatic%20but%20at%20the%20quietest%20levels%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20for%20anyone%20who%20worries%20about%20potential%20bacteria%20from%20humidifiers%2C%20the%20Dyson%20uses%20UV%20light%20to%20kill%20bacteria%20before%20expelling%20the%20(invisible)%20water%20vapor%20into%20the%20air.%20It%20alerts%20you%20when%20it%20needs%20cleaning%20and%20comes%20with%20citrus%20powder%20packets%20for%20that%20purpose%20(you%20can%20also%20buy%20your%20own).%20Fill%20up%20the%20water%20tank%2C%20add%20a%20packet%2C%20and%20hit%20the%20self-clean%20button.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20haven't%20needed%20to%20change%20the%20HEPA%20filter%20yet%2C%20but%20be%20aware%20those%20will%20cost%20you%20an%20additional%20%2480%20every%2012%20months%20or%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20humidifier%20for%20bedrooms%3A%20Levoit%20Classic%20300S%20Humidifier%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Levoit%20Classic%20300S%20Ultrasonic%20Smart%20Humidifier%2C%20the%20best%20humidifier%20for%20bedrooms%20in%202022%2C%20is%20displayed%20next%20to%20plants.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F639b34a227c0a700193e435b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELevoit%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaised%20humidity%20level%20by%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2011%25%20in%204%20hours%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERun%20time%20between%20refills%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2024%20hours%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDimensions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%209.6%20x%207.5%20x%2013.4%20inches%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EColor%20options%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20White%20with%20blue%20or%20gray%20tank%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Operates%20quietly%2C%20small%20footprint%2C%20nightlight%20and%20display-off%20modes%2C%20works%20with%20an%20app%2C%20lasts%20at%20least%2024%20hours%20on%20one%20tank%2C%20easy%20to%20use%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Built-in%20hygrometer%20has%20questionable%20accuracy%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Levoit%20Classic%20300S%20Humidifier%20runs%20as%20quiet%20as%20ambient%20noise%2C%20has%20a%20small%20footprint%2C%20and%20features%20a%20nightlight%2C%20making%20it%20ideal%20for%20the%20bedroom%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-humidifier-for-baby%5C%22%3Ebest%20humidifier%20for%20your%20baby%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Don't%20want%20a%20nightlight%3F%20No%20problem.%20You%20can%20turn%20off%20the%20display%20to%20achieve%20darkness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Levoit%20Classic%20300S%20Humidifier%20did%20an%20excellent%20job%20of%20humidifying%20a%20100-square-foot%20office%20during%20testing.%20On%20a%20particularly%20dry%20winter%20day%2C%20it%20steadily%20increased%20the%20office%20humidity%20by%2011%25%20in%20four%20hours.%20We%20let%20it%20run%20overnight%2C%20and%20the%20humidity%20went%20up%20another%2011%25%20by%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20button%20controls%20on%20the%20unit%20are%20intuitive%2C%20we%20especially%20liked%20that%20you%20can%20monitor%20and%20adjust%20the%20300S%20using%20the%20VeSync%20app%20(available%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fus%2Fapp%2Fvesync%2Fid1289575311%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiOS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.etekcity.vesyncplatform%26hl%3Den_US%26gl%3DUS%26pli%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAndroid%3C%2Fa%3E.)%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20app%20sends%20a%20push%20notification%20when%20the%20tank%20needs%20to%20be%20refilled%20or%20cleaned.%20In%20tests%2C%20the%20humidifier%20ran%20on%20top%20mist%20level%20for%2024%20hours%20before%20needing%20to%20be%20refilled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20operate%20the%20Levoit%20Classic%20300S%20in%20manual%20or%20auto%20mode.%20We%20preferred%20manual%20mode%20because%20the%20built-in%20hygrometer%20showed%20higher%20readings%20than%20the%20hygrometer%20we%20placed%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20room%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20it%20would%20shut%20off%20before%20areas%20further%20from%20the%20unit%20were%20at%20the%20desired%20humidity%20level.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECleaning%20the%20humidifier%20was%20relatively%20easy%20using%20the%20in-app%20step-by-step%20instructions%20and%20the%20included%20brush.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20travel%20humidifier%3A%20Hey%20Dewy%20Wireless%20Facial%20Humidifier%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hey%20Dewy%20Wireless%20Facial%20Humidifier%20turned%20on%2C%20and%20sitting%20on%20a%20shelf%20next%20to%20two%20plants.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F641c7c89b7834100191af49d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHey%20Dewy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaised%20humidity%20level%20by%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%206%25%20over%20seven%20hours%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERun%20time%20between%20refills%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Eight%20hours%20on%20intermittent%20spray%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDimensions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%203%20x%203%20x%207%20inches%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EColor%20options%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Pearl%2C%20blush%2C%20sage%2C%20ocean%2C%20stone%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Optional%20soft%20yellow%20nightlight%2C%20wireless%20option%2C%20can%20use%20tap%20water%2C%20no%20noticeable%20condensation%20leakage%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Not%20as%20quiet%20as%20some%20other%20models%2C%20continuous%20spray%20only%20lasts%20about%20six%20hours%2C%20filter%20needs%20replacing%20every%20four%20to%20six%20months%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravel%20humidifiers%20have%20less%20range%20than%20their%20larger%20counterparts%2C%20but%20their%20smaller%20size%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20bring%20them%20on%20the%20go%20or%20move%20throughout%20your%20home%20as%20needed.%20The%20Hey%20Dewy%20humidifier%20stands%20out%20among%20travel%20humidifiers%20for%20its%20larger%20tank%20size%2C%20powerful%20mist%2C%20and%20long-lasting%20charge.%20It%20didn't%20pump%20up%20the%20overall%20room%20humidity%20quite%20as%20much%20as%20the%20traditional%20humidifiers%20we%20tested%2C%20but%20it%20still%20helped%20add%20plenty%20of%20moisture%20to%20the%20room%2C%20especially%20at%20close%20range.%20After%20seven%20hours%2C%20it%20raised%20the%20humidity%20by%206%25%20in%20a%20four-foot%20range%20%E2%80%94%20and%20by%2013%25%20in%20a%20two-foot%20range.%20So%2C%20it%20may%20be%20a%20good%20option%20if%20you%20plan%20to%20set%20your%20humidifier%20on%20your%20desk%20or%20park%20it%20next%20to%20your%20indoor%20plants.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20humidifier%20doesn't%20make%20a%20lot%20of%20noise%2C%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20hear%20it%20running%20from%20across%20the%20room.%20When%20set%20to%20the%20continuous%20mist%20option%2C%20the%20sound%20worked%20well%20as%20gentle%20white%20noise%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20on-off%20sound%20of%20the%20intermittent%20spray%20could%20be%20distracting%20at%20bedtime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20need%20to%20replace%20the%20humidifier's%20filter%20at%20least%20every%20six%20months.%20But%20since%20the%20filter%20means%20you%20can%20use%20tap%20water%20instead%20of%20having%20to%20purchase%20distilled%20water%2C%20this%20may%20not%20necessarily%20be%20a%20drawback.%20The%20unit%20comes%20pre-assembled%2C%20with%20the%20filter%20in%20place%2C%20and%20once%20charged%2C%20it%20will%20run%20wirelessly%20for%20about%20eight%20hours.%20However%2C%20the%20water%20may%20run%20out%20before%20the%20unit%20needs%20recharging.%20In%20testing%2C%20we%20found%20that%20a%20full%20tank%20of%20water%20(11.3%20fluid%20ounces)%20only%20lasted%20about%20six%20hours%20with%20a%20continuous%20mist%20spray.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20quiet%20humidifier%3A%20Levoit%20OasisMist%20450S%20Smart%20Humidifier%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20sitting%20on%20a%20couch%20using%20her%20cellphone%2C%20next%20to%20a%20Levoit%20OasisMist%20450S%20Smart%20Humidifier%20with%20mist%20shooting%20out%20of%20the%20top.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F641c803db7834100191af56c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22774%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ELevoit%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaised%20humidity%20level%20by%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2016%25%20in%20four%20hours%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ERun%20time%20between%20refills%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Over%2024%20hours%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDimensions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2010.8%20x%206.0%20x%2011.97%20inches%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EColor%20options%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20White%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Extremely%20quiet%20operation%2C%20smart%20features%2C%20produces%20cool%20or%20warm%20mist%2C%20auto%20shutoff%2C%20fully%20dimmable%20display%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Larger%20footprint%2C%20may%20be%20too%20powerful%20for%20smaller%20rooms%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20first%20turn%20the%20Levoit%20OasisMist%20450S%20Smart%20Humidifier%20on%2C%20you'll%20hear%20some%20trickling%20%E2%80%94%20but%20once%20it%20gets%20going%2C%20you%20won't%20hear%20much%20at%20all.%20This%20humidifier%20remains%20extremely%20quiet%20on%20all%20cool%20mist%20settings%2C%20though%20it%20gets%20a%20little%20louder%20when%20producing%20warm%20mist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20quiet%20operation%2C%20this%20machine%20humidifies%20rooms%20very%20efficiently%2C%20with%20no%20noticeable%20condensation%20leakage.%20It%20has%20two%20nozzles%20that%20rotate%20a%20full%20360%C2%B0%2C%20so%20you%20can%20aim%20both%20mist%20plumes%20in%20any%20direction.%20We%20tested%20it%20in%20a%20room%20of%20roughly%20230%20square%20feet%2C%20and%20the%20humidity%20shot%20up%20by%208%25%20within%20just%20one%20hour.%20If%20your%20room%20is%20any%20smaller%20than%20215%20square%20feet%20%E2%80%94%20the%20brand's%20recommended%20lower%20range%20%E2%80%94%20this%20option%20may%20end%20up%20overhumidifying%20your%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20fan%20of%20smart%20features%2C%20this%20humidifier%20comes%20well%20equipped.%20It's%20compatible%20with%20Amazon%20Alexa%20and%20Google%20Voice%2C%20and%20you%20can%20use%20the%20free%20VeSync%20app%20to%20control%20the%20humidifier's%20settings%2C%20check%20the%20humidity%20in%20the%20room%2C%20set%20it%20to%20auto%20mode%2C%20or%20schedule%20shutoff.%20The%20humidifier%20will%20also%20shut%20down%20automatically%20once%20the%20tank%20empties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20tank%20means%20that%20this%20humidifier%20takes%20up%20a%20bit%20more%20space%20in%20your%20room.%20But%20that%20could%20be%20a%20plus%2C%20since%20a%20bigger%20tank%20means%20it%20can%20run%20for%20longer%20between%20refills%3A%20After%2024%20hours%20of%20testing%20on%20medium%20and%20high%20operation%2C%20some%20water%20still%20remained%20in%20the%20tank.%20If%20you%20keep%20the%20humidifier%20on%20low%2C%20it%20can%20run%20for%20up%20to%2045%20hours.%20Another%20bonus%20of%20the%20large%20tank%20is%20a%20smoother%20cleaning%20process.%20What's%20more%2C%20the%20entire%20top%20of%20the%20tank%20comes%20off%2C%20making%20it%20very%20easy%20to%20scrub.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20humidifier%3Cp%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20a%20humidifier%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20consider%20important%20features%20like%20your%20room%20size%2C%20whether%20you%20want%20a%20filter%2C%20and%20mist%20temperature.%20Here%20are%20some%20more%20details%20to%20guide%20your%20shopping%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERoom%20size%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20first%20step%20you%20should%20always%20take%20is%20knowing%20the%20room's%20square%20footage%20you%20want%20to%20primarily%20humidify.%20You%20can%20measure%20your%20room's%20square%20footage%20with%20a%20tape%20measure.%20Then%2C%20read%20up%20on%20the%20humidifier%20you're%20considering%20and%20whether%20the%20brand%20recommends%20it%20for%20small%2C%20medium%2C%20or%20large%20spaces.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20buy%20a%20model%20that%20is%20designed%20for%20a%20larger%20space%2C%20the%20room%20will%20be%20uncomfortably%20humid%20and%20create%20an%20environment%20that%20could%20encourage%20mold%20and%20mildew%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sydney%20Rexroad%2C%20communications%20associate%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aham.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAssociation%20of%20Home%20Appliance%20Manufacturers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20model%20is%20too%20small%2C%20it%20won't%20generate%20adequate%20humidity%20for%20the%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFilter%20versus%20filter-free%20models%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYour%20choice%20here%20may%20depend%20on%20a%20few%20factors%2C%20since%20one%20isn't%20necessarily%20better%20than%20the%20other.%20%26quot%3BFiltered%20humidifiers%20are%20evaporative%20and%20use%20a%20fan%20to%20humidify%20the%20air.%20Filter-free%20models%20will%20put%20a%20mist%20directly%20into%20the%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20Rexroad%20says.%20Additionally%2C%20filter-free%20models%20come%20with%20a%20higher%20risk%20of%20bacteria%20or%20allergens%20getting%20into%20the%20air%2C%20so%20be%20sure%20you%20can%20commit%20to%20cleaning%20it%20thoroughly%20at%20least%20once%20a%20week.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20filters%20need%20to%20be%20replaced%2C%20which%20adds%20an%20additional%20cost%20you%20may%20not%20want%20to%20take%20on.%20Filter%20models%20are%20often%20noisier%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECold%20mist%20versus%20warm%20mist%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAccording%20to%20all%20three%20experts%20we%20spoke%20with%2C%20this%20is%20entirely%20based%20on%20personal%20preference.%20Depending%20on%20your%20main%20use%20for%20the%20humidifier%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20ask%20your%20healthcare%20provider%20before%20making%20a%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmall%20versus%20large%20humidifier%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGenerally%20speaking%2C%20larger%20humidifiers%20have%20bigger%20tanks%2C%20which%20means%20they%20can%20run%20for%20longer%20between%20refills.%20Smaller%20humidifiers%20are%20easier%20to%20move%20throughout%20your%20house%20or%20take%20with%20you%20when%20you%20travel%2C%20but%20some%20may%20not%20last%20an%20entire%20day%20or%20night%20when%20set%20to%20high.%20That%20said%2C%20if%20the%20room%20you%20want%20to%20humidify%20is%20on%20the%20smaller%20side%2C%20a%20larger%20humidifier%20may%20add%20too%20much%20moisture%20to%20the%20air.%20According%20to%20the%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency%20(EPA)%2C%20indoor%20humidity%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Fmold%2Fmold-course-chapter-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshould%20never%20rise%20about%2060%25%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20because%20too-high%20humidity%20can%20lead%20to%20mold%20growth.%20You%20can%20check%20the%20humidity%20in%20your%20room%20with%20a%20hygrometer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdditional%20features%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EHumidifiers%20have%20one%20main%20function%3A%20adding%20moisture%20to%20the%20air.%20If%20you%20want%20a%20humidifier%20that%20performs%20more%20than%20one%20service%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20look%20for%20a%20model%20that%20states%20it%20was%20made%20to%20do%20so.%20We%20recommend%20avoiding%20diffusing%20essential%20oils%2C%20but%20if%20you%20choose%20to%20do%20so%2C%20pick%20a%20model%20explicitly%20made%20for%20that%20dual%20purpose.%20For%20example%2C%20some%20humidifiers%20have%20essential%20oil%20trays%20beneath%20the%20tank%20where%20you%20can%20add%20a%20drop%20or%20two%20of%20your%20chosen%20oil.%20Never%20put%20the%20oil%20directly%20into%20the%20machine.%20%26quot%3BEssential%20oils%2C%20medications%2C%20or%20other%20substances%20can%20damage%20the%20humidifier's%20mechanical%20parts%2C%26quot%3B%20Rexroad%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20test%20humidifiers%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%2010%20popular%20humidifiers%20for%20this%20guide.%20What%20you%20need%20out%20of%20a%20humidifier%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20size%20of%20your%20space%2C%20how%20frequently%20you%20want%20to%20use%20it%2C%20and%20what%20your%20main%20goal%20for%20humidifying%20is.%20However%2C%20some%20universal%20factors%20make%20for%20a%20good%20humidifier.%20Here's%20what%20we%20looked%20for%20while%20testing%20and%20choosing%20our%20top%20picks%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERaised%20humidity%20levels%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThis%20is%20the%20most%20obvious%20and%20most%20important%20factor.%20If%20a%20humidifier%20doesn't%20actually%20raise%20the%20humidity%20levels%20of%20your%20space%20to%20the%20EPA-recommended%2030%25%20to%2050%25%2C%20it%20doesn't%20serve%20its%20main%20function.%20We%20used%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbuythermopro.com%2Fproduct%2Fthermopro-tp-50-temperature-and-humidity-monitor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehygrometer%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20definitively%20test%20the%20humidity%20levels%20of%20our%20space%20before%2C%20during%2C%20and%20after%20using%20each%20humidifier.%20We%20tested%20the%20levels%20right%20near%20the%20humidifiers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20across%20rooms%20of%20various%20sizes.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20setup%20and%20use%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20a%20humidifier%20is%20hard%20to%20figure%20out%2C%20a%20pain%20to%20fill%20up%2C%20or%20doesn't%20last%20a%20full%20day%20or%20night%20on%20one%20tank%20fill%2C%20chances%20are%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20want%20to%20use%20it%20very%20often.%20All%20of%20our%20top%20picks%20take%20five%20minutes%20or%20less%20to%20initially%20set%20up%2C%20are%20easy%20to%20fill%2C%20and%20last%20at%20least%2010%20hours%20on%20one%20tank.%20Some%20can%20even%20last%20days%20on%20a%20single%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20cleaning%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Without%20proper%20cleaning%2C%20humidifiers%20can%20grow%20mold%20or%20bacteria%20that%20can%20then%20be%20dispersed%20into%20your%20home.%20We%20did%20a%20deep%20clean%20of%20every%20humidifier%20we%20chose%20and%20found%20it%20to%20be%20an%20easy%20process%20for%20all%20of%20our%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExtra%20features%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Some%20humidifiers%20come%20with%20fancy%20extras%20that%20range%20from%20simple%20night-light%20settings%20to%20app%20and%20voice%20control.%20These%20extras%20were%20taken%20into%20account%20to%20discern%20if%20they%20actually%20provided%20additional%20value%20and%20ease%20of%20use.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELongevity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We've%20tested%20most%20of%20these%20humidifiers%20for%20about%20two%20months%20and%20have%20not%20run%20into%20issues%20with%20the%20top%20choices.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20test%20to%20ensure%20they%20hold%20up%20over%20time%20and%20no%20serious%20issues%20arise%2C%20such%20as%20mold%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHumidifier%20FAQs%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20humidifiers%20good%20for%20the%20lungs%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Purvi%20Parikh%2C%20an%20adult%20and%20pediatric%20allergist%20and%20immunologist%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fallergyasthmanetwork.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAllergy%20%26amp%3B%20Asthma%20Network%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20says%20dry%20air%20can%20make%20allergy%20and%20asthma%20symptoms%20worse.%20Introducing%20a%20humidifier%20will%20moisten%20the%20air%2C%20which%20may%20help%20protect%20your%20lungs%20from%20irritants.%20But%20it's%20essential%20to%20keep%20the%20humidifier%20clean%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Findoor-air-quality-iaq%2Fuse-and-care-home-humidifiers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevent%20a%20buildup%20of%20mold%20and%20bacteria%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Additionally%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20only%20use%20distilled%20water%20in%20your%20humidifier%2C%20unless%20the%20device%20specifically%20says%20to%20use%20tap%20water.%20Tap%20water%20can%20release%20minerals%20into%20the%20air%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mcgill.ca%2Foss%2Farticle%2Fcritical-thinking-health%2Fquestions-abound-safety-humidifiers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperts%3C%2Fa%3E%20don't%20yet%20know%20the%20long-term%20health%20effects%20of%20breathing%20in%20these%20particles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20a%20cool%20mist%20or%20warm%20mist%20humidifier%20better%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWarm%20and%20cool%20mist%20humidifiers%20work%20equally%20well%20to%20add%20moisture%20to%20the%20air%2C%20so%20Rexroad%20and%20Parikh%20suggest%20letting%20your%20personal%20preferences%20guide%20you%20in%20this%20decision.%20If%20a%20doctor%20or%20other%20healthcare%20professional%20recommends%20using%20a%20humidifier%2C%20check%20with%20them%20to%20find%20out%20if%20a%20cool%20mist%20or%20warm%20mist%20would%20help%20you%20get%20the%20most%20relief.%20You%20may%20also%20prefer%20a%20warm%20mist%20humidifier%20during%20the%20colder%20months.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinic.org%2Fdiseases-conditions%2Fcommon-cold%2Fexpert-answers%2Fcool-mist-humidifiers%2Ffaq-20058199%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Mayo%20Clinic%20warns%20against%20using%20warm-mist%20humidifiers%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20babies%20and%20children%2C%20since%20they%20pose%20a%20risk%20of%20burns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20most%20effective%20type%20of%20humidifier%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20effective%20humidifier%20should%20raise%20the%20humidity%20in%20a%20room%20without%20overhumidifying%20the%20room.%20All%20of%20our%20picks%20raised%20room%20humidity%20by%20at%20least%206%25%20over%20eight%20hours.%20However%2C%20since%20experts%20recommend%20keeping%20the%20level%20of%20humidity%20in%20your%20home%20between%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinic.org%2Fdiseases-conditions%2Fcommon-cold%2Fin-depth%2Fhumidifiers%2Fart-20048021%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%25%20and%2050%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20most%20effective%20humidifier%20for%20you%20will%20help%20maintain%20this%20humidity%20level.%20If%20you'd%20like%20to%20use%20your%20humidifier%20to%20help%20ease%20congestion%2C%20dry%20skin%2C%20and%20other%20symptoms%2C%20a%20healthcare%20professional%20can%20provide%20more%20guidance%20on%20choosing%20a%20humidifier%20for%20your%20specific%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20humidifiers%20are%20best%20for%20winter%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20humidifier%20during%20the%20winter%20can%20be%20helpful%20because%20indoor%20heating%20can%20cause%20the%20air%20to%20dry%20out%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flunginstitute.com%2Fabout%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChristine%20Kingsley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20advanced%20practice%20registered%20nurse%20and%20the%20Health%20and%20Wellness%20Director%20of%20the%20Lung%20Institute.%20%26quot%3BHumidifiers%20add%20moisture%20to%20the%20air%2C%20alleviating%20symptoms%20of%20dry%20skin%2C%20dry%20throat%2C%20and%20sinus%20congestion%2C%26quot%3B%20Kingsley%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20prefer%20warm-mist%20humidifiers%20during%20the%20colder%20months.%20These%20humidifiers%20disperse%20vapor%20by%20heating%20water%2C%20so%20they%20can%20add%20some%20extra%20warmth%20to%20chilly%20rooms.%20But%20Kingsley%20cautions%20that%20warm%20mist%20can%20create%20an%20extremely%20humid%20environment%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20mold%20and%20bacteria.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20I%20need%20an%20air%20purifier%20and%20humidifier%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fshould-you-buy-all-in-one-humidifier-air-purifier%5C%22%3Eair%20purifier%3C%2Fa%3E%20removes%20pollutants%20from%20the%20air%2C%20helping%20reduce%20potentially%20irritating%20particles%20like%20dust%2C%20pollen%2C%20and%20pet%20dander%2C%20says%20John%20Landry%2C%20licensed%20registered%20respiratory%20therapist%20and%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.respiratorytherapyzone.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERespiratory%20Therapy%20Zone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20humidifier%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20adds%20moisture%20to%20the%20air%2C%20Landry%20says%2C%20which%20can%20help%20soothe%20dry%20skin%2C%20sinus%20congestion%2C%20and%20respiratory%20issues.%20You%20may%20benefit%20from%20an%20air%20purifier%20if%20you%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F29549698%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseasonal%20allergies%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F29549698%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easthma%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20a%20humidifier%20may%20offer%20relief%20if%20you%20live%20in%20a%20drier%20climate%20or%20have%20dry%20skin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhich%20humidifiers%20are%20safe%20for%20children%20and%20babies%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Academy%20of%20Pediatrics%20considers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthychildren.org%2FEnglish%2Fsafety-prevention%2Fat-home%2FPages%2FMake-Babys-Room-Safe.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecool%20mist%20humidifiers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20the%20safest%20option%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-humidifier-for-baby%5C%22%3Ebabies%20and%20young%20children%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Warm%20mist%20humidifiers%20work%20by%20producing%20steam%2C%20which%20can%20be%20hot%20enough%20to%20burn%20a%20curious%20toddler%20who%20tries%20to%20touch%20it.%20Whichever%20type%20of%20humidifier%20you%20choose%2C%20always%20take%20care%20to%20set%20it%20someplace%20out%20of%20reach%20of%20children%20and%20pets.%20Another%20important%20part%20of%20humidifier%20safety%20is%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.childrenscolorado.org%2Fconditions-and-advice%2Fparenting%2Fparenting-articles%2Fdanger-of-humidifiers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonly%20distilled%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20free%20of%20minerals%20that%20may%20evaporate%20into%20your%20household%20air%2C%20and%20cleaning%20the%20unit%20regularly%20with%20vinegar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20often%20do%20you%20need%20to%20clean%20a%20humidifier%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EPA%20advises%20cleaning%20your%20humidifier%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epa.gov%2Findoor-air-quality-iaq%2Fuse-and-care-home-humidifiers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevery%20third%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%203%25%20solution%20of%20hydrogen%20peroxide.%20You%20can%20also%20clean%20your%20humidifier%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.childrenscolorado.org%2Fconditions-and-advice%2Fparenting%2Fparenting-articles%2Fdanger-of-humidifiers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evinegar%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20clean%20your%20humidifier%20properly%2C%20first%20unplug%20the%20unit%20and%20then%20use%20a%20scrubbing%20brush%20to%20clean%20all%20surfaces%20that%20touch%20water.%20If%20you%20use%20any%20chemicals%20to%20clean%20your%20humidifier%2C%20take%20care%20to%20rinse%20it%20several%20times%20with%20clean%20tap%20water%20before%20using%20it%20again.%20You%20can%20check%20the%20instruction%20booklet%20that%20came%20with%20your%20humidifier%20for%20additional%20cleaning%20instructions%20specific%20to%20your%20unit.%20If%20you%20don't%20intend%20to%20use%20your%20humidifier%20for%20a%20while%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20clean%20it%20out%20and%20allow%20it%20to%20fully%20dry%20before%20you%20store%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-humidifier%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710338806000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F616df77e41af0d00193f2f01%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-humidifier%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20humidifiers%20add%20moisture%20back%20into%20your%20home%20and%20offer%20health%20benefits%2C%20too.%20We%20test%20how%20they%20increase%20humidity%20plus%20ease%20of%20use%20and%20care.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jbr