us-one-says-haryana-mp-brijendra-singh-5225434%5C%22%3Ebroke%20rank%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanohar-lal-khattar-bjp-jjp-haryana-lok-sabha-elections-dushyant-chautala-bjp-may-end-haryana-alliance-ml-khattar-to-fight-lok-sabha-polls-sources-5222832%5C%22%3EJannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20had%20supported%20it%20in%20the%20previous%20assembly%20election.%20The%20BJP%2C%20facing%20anger%20from%20Jats%2C%20Dalits%20and%20Muslims%2C%20who%20account%20for%2050%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20was%20pushed%20to%2040%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20assembly%20polls-seven%20less%20than%20in%202014%20and%20six%20short%20of%20a%20majority-but%20eventually%20went%20on%20to%20form%20a%20government%2C%20courtesy%20a%20post-poll%20alliance%20with%20the%20JJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETried%20%26amp%3B%20Tested%20Strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20of%20guard%20is%20in%20line%20with%20a%20similar%20strategy%20the%20BJP%20has%20followed%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Tripura%20and%20Uttarakhand%2C%20where%20it%20replaced%20its%20sitting%20chief%20ministers%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20neutralise%20leader-%20or%20government-related%20anti-incumbency.%20The%20strategy%20reaped%20dividends%20in%20the%20three%20states%2C%20though%20it%20didn't%20help%20the%20party%20in%20Karnataka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENayab%20Singh%20Saini%2C%20the%20new%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%2C%20hails%20from%20an%20Extremely%20Backward%20Class%20(EBC).%20With%20that%20choice%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20has%20pushed%20forward%20with%20its%20strategy%20of%20looking%20past%20the%20dominant%20Jat%20caste%20in%20Haryana%20and%20instead%20consolidating%20the%20non-Jat%20vote%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20General%20category%20and%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC).%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20BJP%20hopes%20that%20the%20vote%20from%20the%20Jat%20community%2C%20which%20constitutes%20over%20a%20fifth%20of%20the%20state's%20population%20and%20is%20presumably%20displeased%20with%20the%20party%20after%20the%20farmers'%20and%20wrestlers'%20protests%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Agniveer%20scheme%2C%20will%20get%20split%20between%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%20and%20the%20JJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20outgoing%20chief%20minister%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fway-manohar-ji-has-worked-tirelessly-pms-praise-for-old-friend-5219304%5C%22%3EManohar%20Lal%20Khattar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%C2%A0he%20is%20expected%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20now%20and%20move%20to%20the%20Centre.%20The%20irony%20is%20that%20he%20lost%20his%20post%20just%20a%20day%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20fondly%20recalled%20his%20friendship%20with%20him%20in%20a%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELooking%20Past%20The%20Dominant%20Caste%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20now%20is%20among%20the%20few%20states%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20experimented%20with%20installing%20chief%20ministers%20who%20don't%20come%20from%20a%20dominant%20community.%20In%202014%2C%20it%20had%20put%20at%20the%20helm%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20a%20non-Maratha%2C%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Raghubar%20Das%2C%20a%20non-tribal%2C%20in%20Jharkhand.%20The%20experiment%20failed%20in%20both%20states%2C%20with%20the%20party%20losing%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20being%20unable%20to%20form%20a%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%20subsequent%20elections%20in%202019.%20Correcting%20its%20error%2C%20the%20BJP%20finally%20installed%20a%20Maratha%20chief%20minister%20in%20Maharashtra%20in%202022.%20Nonetheless%2C%20it%20has%20given%20the%20strategy%20another%20try%20in%20Haryana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20immediate%20threat%20to%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Haryana%20as%20it%20enjoys%20the%20support%20of%20independents%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Lokhit%20Party%20(HLP)%20as%20well%20as%20a%20few%20MLAs%20of%20the%20JJP.%20Though%20the%20latter%20issued%20a%20whip%20to%20its%20leaders%20to%20abstain%20from%20voting%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20the%20trust%20vote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20parting%20ways%20was%20the%20JJP's%20demand%20for%20a%20few%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20when%20the%20BJP%20wanted%20to%20contest%20alone.%20The%20fact%20that%20it%20could%20not%20have%20forged%20a%20tie-up%20with%20the%20Congress%20or%20the%20INLD%20emboldened%20the%20BJP%20to%20take%20the%20risk%20of%20ending%20the%20alliance.%20Jats%2C%20in%20any%20case%2C%20had%20been%20unhappy%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabhay-singh-chautala-dushyant-chautala-haryana-uncles-betrayal-dig-at-dushyant-chautala-as-bjp-revamps-haryana-cabinet-5224869%5C%22%3EJJP%20chief%20Dushyant%20Chautala%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20having%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP.%20In%20fact%2C%20recently%2C%20Brijendra%20Singh%2C%20a%20Jat%20MP%2C%20quit%20the%20BJP%20and%20crossed%20over%20to%20the%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESplitting%20The%20Jat%20Vote%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20swept%20Haryana%20in%20the%20last%20two%20general%20elections%2C%20winning%20seven%20seats%20in%202014%2C%20and%20later%2C%20all%2010%20in%202019.%20This%20was%20despite%20having%20trailed%20amongst%20Jats%2C%20whose%20votes%20were%20split%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20INLD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%20(CSDS)%20show%20that%20in%20the%202014%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%20just%2019%25%20of%20Jat%20support%2C%20against%2054%25%20for%20the%20INLD%20and%2021%25%20for%20the%20Congress.%20The%20following%20numbers%20illustrate%20the%20point%20further%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%202014%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%20just%2017%25%20of%20%C2%A0Jat%20votes%20against%2042%25%20for%20the%20INLD%20and%2024%25%20for%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20got%2039%25%20of%20the%20Jat%20vote%2C%20the%20Congress%20got%2040%25%20(Axis%20My%20India)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20however%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20able%20to%20consolidate%20its%20vote%20base%20among%20the%20upper%20castes%20and%20OBCs%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%202014%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%20just%2051%25%20of%20upper-caste%20and%2043%25%20of%20OBC%20support%20(CSDS).%20Those%20figures%20remained%20similar%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20too%20that%20year%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20BJP's%20upper-caste%20vote%20share%20climbed%20to%2069%25%2C%20and%20that%20of%20OBCs%20to%2070%25%20(Axis%20My%20India)%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Modi%20Factor%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20banking%20on%20the%20'Modi%20magic'%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20While%20for%2037%25%20of%20voters%2C%20the%20PM%20face%20was%20the%20most%20important%20factor%20in%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20corresponding%20number%20for%20Haryana%20in%202019%20was%2056%25.%20The%20party%20also%20hopes%20that%20with%20Dushyant%20Chautala%20now%20contesting%20alone%2C%20a%20section%20of%20the%20Jat%20vote%20will%20go%20to%20the%20JJP%2C%20thus%20upsetting%20the%20Congress's%20calculations%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20could%20have%20faced%20trouble%20if%20it%20were%20facing%20any%20regional%20party%20in%20the%20state.%20But%20since%20it's%20Congress%20that's%20in%20the%20key%20rival%20post%2C%20strategists%20are%20confident%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20be%20able%20to%20repeat%20its%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20act%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20saga%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20tactical%20plan%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20even%20calling%20it%20a%20'match-fixing'%20between%20the%20JJP%20and%20BJP.%20It%20now%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20much%20Jat%20support%20Chautala%20is%20able%20to%20pull.%20The%20BJP%20is%20hoping%20for%20some%20sympathy%20votes%20to%20come%20his%20way%2C%20given%20it%20was%20not%20Chautala%20who%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20alliance.%20The%20Congress%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20is%20optimistic%20that%20Jats%20would%20not%20forgive%20the%20JJP%20and%20Dushyant%20for%20siding%20with%20the%20BJP%20for%20over%20four%20years%2C%20and%20would%20instead%20vote%20for%20the%20grand%20old%20party.%20Interesting%20times%20ahead%20for%20Haryana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710337500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fbpdjkd8_nayab-singh-saini-haryana-chief-minister_625x300_12_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fharyana-will-bjps-experiment-with-a-non-jat-chief-minister-nayab-singh-saini-pay-off-5231949%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Haryana%20now%20is%20among%20the%20few%20states%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20experimented%20with%20installing%20chief%20ministers%20who%20don't%20come%20from%20a%20dominant%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fharyana-will-bjps-experiment-with-a-non-jat-chief-minister-nayab-singh-saini-pay-off-5231949%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fharyana-will-bjps-experiment-with-a-non-jat-chief-minister-nayab-singh-saini-pay-off-5231949%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fh