ob%2C%20Clay%20Coomer%20would%20sometimes%20see%20a%20colleague%20in%20the%20hallway%20and%20have%20a%20quick%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20would%20be%20like%2C%20'Hey%2C%20you%20need%20one%3F'%26quot%3B%20Coomer%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20item%20in%20question%20was%20a%20Zyn%2C%20a%20brand%20of%20nicotine%20pouch%20that%20users%20often%20place%20under%20their%20lips%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealth.unl.edu%2Fnicotine-pouches-are-they-safer-chewing-smoking-or-vaping%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eget%20a%20boost%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Coomer%20and%20his%20former%20coworker%20would%20each%20share%20their%20stash%20when%20the%20other's%20was%20running%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Coomer%2C%20who's%2036%20and%20works%20in%20marketing%2C%20popping%20in%20a%20Zyn%20is%20just%20sometimes%20how%20he%20gets%20hard%20work%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20need%20to%20have%20a%20challenging%20conversation%20with%20somebody%20or%20if%20I%20need%20to%20work%20on%20something%20that's%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20important%20than%20other%20things%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0like%20it's%20just%20a%20part%20of%20the%20routine%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoomer%20isn't%20alone.%20BI%20spoke%20with%20a%20handful%20of%20men%20in%20various%20fields%20who%20are%20relying%20on%20the%20lift%20they%20get%20from%20the%20nicotine%20as%20a%20way%20to%20get%20through%20the%20day%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0especially%20the%20hardest%20things%20that%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20tackle%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0without%20the%20mess%20and%20health%20risks%20of%20chewing%20tobacco%20or%20cigarettes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221158%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Clay%20Coomer%20on%20a%20boat%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb68876080194819fe3da2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221544%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClay%20Coomer%20often%20pops%20in%20a%20Zyn%20when%20he%20has%20to%20get%20hard%20work%20done.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Clay%20Coomer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20had%20used%20nicotine%20or%20tobacco%20products%20previously%20and%20described%20turning%20to%20Zyn%20because%20they%20viewed%20it%20as%20a%20healthier%20or%20cleaner%20alternative%20to%20the%20likes%20of%20dip%2C%20vaping%2C%20or%20cigarettes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rise%20of%20Zyn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EZyn%20has%20been%20available%20for%20sale%20in%20the%20US%20since%202014%20but%20has%20seen%20wider%20popularity%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzyn-nicotine-pouches-huge-increase-us-shipments-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShipments%20of%20the%20nicotine%20pouches%20in%20the%20US%20in%202023%20were%20up%2062%25%20year-over-year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20while%20product%20shipments%20can%20outpace%20consumer%20sales%2C%20Tobacco%20giant%20Philip%20Morris%20International%2C%20which%20owns%20Zyn's%20manufacturer%2C%20Swedish%20Match%2C%20forecasts%20even%20greater%20shipping%20volume%20this%20year.%20Zyn%20pouches%20have%20found%20favor%20with%20everyone%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-streets-underground-drug-abuse-culture-cocaine-adderall-zyn-mushrooms-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-powered%20Wall%20Street%20traders%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchuck-schumer-nicotine-zyn-republican-right-wing-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETucker%20Carlson%20and%20GOP%20lawmakers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20even%20%26quot%3BZynfluencers%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20post%20videos%20on%20social%20media%20of%20themselves%20slipping%20pouches%20under%20their%20lips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%2028-year-old%20corporate%20performance%20management%20consultant%20who%20previously%20used%20dip%20says%20he%20views%20Zyn%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20lesser%20of%20all%20the%20evils%26quot%3B%20among%20nicotine%20and%20tobacco%20products%20in%20terms%20of%20health%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20sources%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20because%20they%20didn't%20want%20to%20jeopardize%20future%20job%20prospects%2C%20but%20their%20identities%20are%20known%20to%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaymond%20Niaura%2C%20chair%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Epidemiology%20at%20New%20York%20University%20and%20an%20expert%20on%20tobacco%20dependence%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20there%20is%20risk%20of%20addiction%20with%20any%20product%20containing%20nicotine.%20(The%20FDA%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ftobacco-products%2Fproducts-ingredients-components%2Fregulation-and-enforcement-non-tobacco-nicotine-ntn-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissued%20a%20similar%20warning%3C%2Fa%3E.)%20Niaura%20added%20that%20pouches%20tend%20to%20deliver%20less%20nicotine%20than%20cigarettes%2C%20which%20he%20said%20are%20more%20addictive.%20Instead%2C%20the%20pouches%20are%20more%20akin%20to%20nicotine%20replacement%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENiaura%20said%2C%20in%20general%2C%20a%20nicotine%20pouch%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20clean%20product%26quot%3B%20yet%20still%20could%20carry%20risks%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.heart.org%2Fen%2Fhealthy-living%2Fhealthy-lifestyle%2Fquit-smoking-tobacco%2Fhow-smoking-and-nicotine-damage-your-body%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNicotine%2520is%2520a%2520dangerous%2520and%2Clead%2520to%2520a%2520heart%2520attack%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENicotine%2C%20for%20example%2C%20can%20increase%20heart%20rate%20and%20blood%20pressure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20someone%20at%20risk%20for%20cardiovascular%20disease%20might%20want%20to%20be%20particularly%20careful%20using%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20early%20days.%20It's%20hard%20to%20say%20for%20sure%20where%20these%20products%20fit%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20how%20addictive%20products%20like%20Zyn%20might%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'hand%20of%20God'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20using%20a%20pouch%20at%20work%2C%20nicotine%20pouches%20tend%20to%20be%20so%20small%20they're%20nearly%20invisible%20to%20others%2C%20which%20is%20another%20part%20of%20the%20appeal%20for%20some%20users.%20Not%20that%20it's%20such%20a%20big%20deal%20anyway%2C%20several%20users%20told%20BI%2C%20because%20the%20pouches%20don't%20contain%20tobacco.%20So%20there's%20not%20the%20same%20stigma%20there%20might%20be%20with%20tobacco%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20really%20cares%2C%26quot%3B%20Coomer%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20using%20Zyn%20at%20startups.%20When%20he%20worked%20for%20a%20big%20blue%20chip%20company%2C%20he%20was%20somewhat%20more%20guarded%20about%20pulling%20out%20his%20canister%20of%20Zyn%20or%20keeping%20it%20in%20his%20pocket%20so%20it%20didn't%20look%20like%20a%20container%20of%20dip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENate%20Palmer%20is%20a%20personal%20trainer%2C%20podcaster%2C%20and%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmilliondollarbodylabs.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMillion%20Dollar%20Body%20Labs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20works%20remotely%20with%20clients%20to%20improve%20their%20fitness%20and%20overall%20health.%20He%20chewed%20nicotine%20gum%20about%20a%20decade%20ago%20as%20a%20pick-me-up.%20But%20after%20not%20using%20nicotine%20for%20a%20while%2C%20he%20wasn't%20prepared%20for%20the%20hit%20he%20got%20when%20he%20popped%20a%206%20mg%20pouch%20of%20Zyn.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20the%20hand%20of%20God%20on%20my%20central%20nervous%20system.%20I%20was%20just%20feeling%20amazing.%20And%20then%20I%20just%20had%20to%20go%20throw%20up.%26quot%3B%20Palmer%20has%20since%20downshifted%20to%20the%203%20mg%20pouches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he%20holds%20himself%20to%20four%20pouches%20a%20day.%20And%20while%20he%20said%20he's%20not%20quite%20addicted%2C%20he%20does%20miss%20it%20when%20he%20hasn't%20done%20it%20for%20a%20while%2C%20he%20said.%20For%20now%2C%20it's%20become%20part%20of%20his%20routine%20when%20he%20has%20to%20concentrate%20on%20something%20demanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nate%20Palmer%20in%20a%20gym%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb6a326080194819fe4079%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENate%20Palmer%20uses%20Zyn%20when%20he%20has%20to%20do%20deep%20work.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Nate%20Palmer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20basically%20will%20just%20do%20it%20now%20for%2C%20like%2C%20podcasts%20or%20if%20I've%20got%20like%20a%20sales%20call%20or%20something%20where%20I'm%20like%2C%20I%20need%20to%20get%20dialed%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20doing%20it%20like%20at%20kid's%20birthday%20parties%20where%20I'm%20like%2C%20'I%20don't%20want%20to%20talk%20to%20these%20people.%20I%20need%20to%20be%20more%20friendly.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalmer%20sees%20using%20Zyn%20as%20an%20important%20part%20of%20his%20ritual%20around%20essential%20work.%20He%20advises%20his%20clients%20to%20focus%20on%20creating%20rituals%20to%20pair%20something%20difficult%20with%20something%20that%20can%20act%20as%20a%20reward%2C%20a%20concept%20called%20temptation%20coupling.%20In%20his%20case%2C%20his%20ritual%20helps%20him%20get%20through%20major%20tasks%20at%20work.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20sit%20down%20when%20I%20try%20to%20do%20deep%20work%2C%20like%20I%20kind%20of%20have%20a%20ritual%20now%20where%20I%20put%20on%20some%20binaural%20beats%20from%20Spotify%2C%20I'll%20put%20a%20Zyn%20in%20and%20then%2C%20you%20know%2C%20I'll%20make%20sure%20that%20I%20have%20my%20list%20of%20stuff%20I%20need%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20over%20the%20hump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChandler%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20software%20engineer%20who%20started%20smoking%20cigarettes%20in%20his%20teens%20before%20switching%20to%20vaping%20and%20now%20Zyns%2C%20said%20the%20pouches%20give%20him%20a%20similar%20%26quot%3Bdopamine%20rush%26quot%3B%20without%20%26quot%3Bfeeling%20the%20burn%20in%20your%20lungs%20and%20in%20your%20throat%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20did%20with%20those%20other%20products.%20Chandler%20works%20from%20home%20but%20says%20his%20boss%20is%20aware%20of%20his%20Zyn%20use%20at%20work%20and%20has%20no%20issue%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I'm%20really%20trying%20to%20focus%20and%20use%20my%20brain%20and%20think%20hard%2C%20I'm%20just%20pounding%20through%20the%20pouches%20and%20then%20that%20kind%20of%20tapers%20off%20as%20the%20workday%20ends%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pops%20a%20Zyn%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20thing%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20mornings%20and%20estimates%20he%20goes%20through%20a%20little%20over%20a%20can%2C%20which%20contains%2015%20pouches%2C%20each%20workday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20that%20once%20that%20nicotine%20buzz%20wears%20off%2C%20it's%20like%20a%20kind%20of%20background%20noise%20in%20your%20brain%20that's%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I%20should%20take%20another.'%20It%20just%20grows%20the%20longer%20that%20you%20don't%20have%20it%2C%20and%20that%20in%20and%20of%20itself%20becomes%20distracting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20it%20is%20not%20something%20that%20helps%20you%20focus%2C%20it's%20that%20not%20taking%20it%20really%20can%20take%20away%20from%20your%20focus.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%2024-year-old%20senior%20analyst%20who%20was%20a%20self-described%20%26quot%3Bpart%20of%20the%20JUUL%20population%26quot%3B%20before%20switching%20to%20Zyn%20says%20the%20pouches%20%26quot%3Bget%20me%20into%20the%20right%20headspace%20and%20keep%20me%20focused%20more%20or%20less.%26quot%3B%20He%20works%20five%20days%20a%20week%20in%20the%20office%20but%20says%20there's%20no%20stigma%20around%20using%20it%20there.%20He%20starts%20his%20days%20taking%20a%20Zyn%20with%20his%20morning%20coffee%20and%20has%20between%205%20to%2010%20in%20the%20course%20of%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20understand%20that%20nicotine%20is%20an%20addictive%20drug%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20it's%20just%20like%20when%20you%20have%20a%20Zyn%20in%2C%20it%20just%20helps%20you%20focus%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Dashiell%2C%20a%20Philip%20Morris%20spokesperson%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%20that%20Zyn%20is%20intended%20for%20people%2021%20and%20over%20who%20are%20using%20nicotine%20and%20wish%20to%20continue%20doing%20so.%20He%20said%20the%20best%20thing%20someone%20with%20health%20concerns%20can%20do%20is%20to%20quit%20or%20not%20ever%20use%20nicotine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNicotine%20is%20addictive%20and%20not%20risk-free%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20high%20levels%20of%20other%20harmful%20chemicals%20in%20cigarette%20smoke%20that%20are%20the%20primary%20cause%20of%20tobacco-related%20diseases%E2%80%94not%20nicotine%2C%26quot%3B%20Dashiell%20wrote.%20The%20company%20has%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fphilipmorrisinternational.gcs-web.com%2Fstatic-files%2Fa86c6d92-8e5b-4e8e-ae88-3914c1f92c03%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaverage%20Zyn%20user%20is%2039%3C%2Fa%3E%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20plan%20to%20ditch%20nicotine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20of%20the%20Zyn%20users%20said%20they're%20using%20the%20pouches%20as%20a%20stepping%20stone%20on%20the%20path%20to%20eventually%20get%20off%20nicotine%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%20in%20the%20future%20I%20would%20like%20to%20not%20be%20a%20nicotine%20user.%20I%20think%20when%20I%20was%20young%20and%20JUULs%20were%20the%20big%20thing%20and%20then%20all%20that%20stuff%20happened%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20I%20would%20say%20got%20stuck%20with%20the%20nicotine%20addiction%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analyst%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjuul-e-cigarettes-ban-us-fda-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFDA's%20JUUL%20ban%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20being%20able%20to%20more%20or%20less%20wean%20off%20on%20Zyns%20seems%20a%20lot%20easier%20than%20the%20JUULs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChandler%20too%20is%20fine%20using%20Zyn%20for%20now%2C%20at%20work%20and%20otherwise%2C%20as%20he%20works%20on%20reducing%20his%20nicotine%20use%20but%20also%20wants%20to%20quit%20it%20eventually.%20His%20reasoning%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20health%20hits%20that%20you%20take%20from%20doing%20it%20and%20just%20how%20much%20you%20come%20to%20rely%20on%20it%2C%20where%20you%20would%20go%20nuts%20if%20you%20didn't%20have%20access%20to%20it%20for%20a%20few%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20masked%20a%20lot%20by%20how%20OK%20it%20is%20in%20culture%2C%20but%20it's%20an%20addiction%20and%20I%20feel%20bad%20for%20anybody%20that%20gets%20sucked%20into%20it%20because%20it's%20awful%2C%20awful%20to%20quit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20could%20go%20back%20and%20never%20start%20using%20nicotine%2C%20I%20would.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzyn-pouches-become-popular-some-workers-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710337035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f0728690413ab8e1dbc6c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzyn-pouches-become-popular-some-workers-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Zyn%2C%20a%20type%20nicotine%20pouch%2C%20is%20gaining%20popularity%20with%20some%20workers%20looking%20to%20get%20a%20boost.%20But%2C%20like%20any%20nicotine%20product%2C%20there's%20risk%20of%20addiction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sjackson%40insider.com%20(Sarah%20Jackson%2CTim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzyn-pouches-become-popular-some-workers-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20way%20to%20help%20American%20homebuyers%3F%20Do%20what%20the%20Dutch%20do.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Homes%20along%20a%20canal%20in%20Amsterdam.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb53166080194819fe1f27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221631%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDutch-style%20mortgages%20offer%20something%20American%20mortgages%20don't%3A%20automatically%20lower%20interest%20rates%20as%20the%20loan%20is%20paid%20off.%3Cp%3EYasonya%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAmericans%20are%20having%20a%20hard%20time%20affording%20homes%20as%20prices%20and%20interest%20rates%20have%20soared.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20different%20kind%20of%20mortgage%20could%20help%20address%20the%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%2C%20including%20borrowers%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20are%20looking%20to%20Dutch-style%20mortgages.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESoaring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-mortgage-refinance-rates-today-wednesday-6-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterest%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20home%20prices%20have%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-outlook-unaffordable-charts-mortgage-rates-home-prices-economy-2024-1%23%3A~%3Atext%3DRedfin%2520data%2520shows%2520just%252015.5%2Cfrom%252020.7%2525%2520the%2520year%2520prior.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomeownership%20unattainable%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20many%20Americans.%20While%20they%20wait%20for%20those%20figures%20to%20come%20down%2C%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20problem%20could%20be%20found%20in%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dutch%20offer%20home%20mortgages%20with%20evolving%20interest%20rates%20that%20can%20automatically%20decrease%20over%20time.%20The%20thinking%20is%20that%20as%20the%20loan%20gets%20older%20and%20the%20ratio%20of%20the%20amount%20owed%20to%20the%20home's%20value%20improves%20%E2%80%94%20through%20paying%20off%20the%20loan%20or%20any%20increase%20in%20the%20property's%20value%20%E2%80%94%20the%20risk%20associated%20with%20the%20loan%20decreases.%20As%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20loan%20improves%20for%20the%20lender%2C%20there%20is%20less%20of%20a%20need%20to%20offset%20the%20risks%20with%20higher%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20particular%20style%20of%20loan%20could%20help%20many%20Americans%2C%20both%20homeowners%20who%20want%20to%20move%20and%20first-time%20homebuyers%20who%20are%20concerned%20about%20high%20current%20and%20future%20interest%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20obvious%20benefit%20to%20home%20buyers%20is%20that%20the%20interest%20rate%20on%20a%20loan%20goes%20down%20over%20time%20without%20having%20to%20pay%20the%20costs%20associated%20with%20refinancing%2C%20which%20can%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Faverage-refinance-closing-costs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethousands%20of%20dollars%20each%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20mortgage%20interest%20rates%20drop%2C%20the%20improved%20rate%20could%20be%20even%20better%20than%20a%20refinance%2C%20since%20a%20buyer%20with%20a%20Dutch-style%20mortgage%20would%20have%20the%20compounded%20benefits%20of%20lower%20rates%20and%20a%20less%20risky%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20type%20of%20mortgage%20works%20well%20in%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20mortgage%20systems%20vary%20widely%20across%20borders.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ftypes-of-mortgage-loans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20most%20mortgages%20are%20bought%20and%20sold%20on%20a%20secondary%20market%20%E2%80%94%20with%20lenders%20and%20investors%20buying%20mortgages%20and%20servicing%20rights%20%E2%80%94%20making%20it%20tricky%20to%20change%20to%20individual%20loans%20over%20time.%20However%2C%20other%20countries%20are%20taking%20notice%3A%20The%20Dutch%20mortgage%20lender%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dmfco.nl%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDMFCO%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%20began%20offering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fmoney%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F08%2Fmortgages-cut-rates-april-mortgages%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDutch-style%20mortgages%20in%20the%20UK%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20type%20of%20loan%20would%20likely%20bring%20more%20buyers%20to%20the%20market%2C%20but%20Lindsey%20Harn%20of%20the%20Lindsey%20Harn%20Group%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20firm%20in%20San%20Luis%20Obispo%20County%2C%20California%2C%20believes%20it%20could%20also%20entice%20more%20people%20to%20sell%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20this%20would%20allow%20more%20middle-aged%20sellers%20to%20consider%20selling%20and%20giving%20up%20their%20current%20low-interest%20rate%20to%20buy%20another%20house%2C%20whether%20that%20is%20bigger%20or%20smaller%2C%26quot%3B%20Harn%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20would%20be%20a%20huge%20benefit%20because%C2%A0I%20think%20it%20would%20give%20longtime%20homeowners%20the%20confidence%20to%20move%20and%20not%20get%20stuck%20with%20a%20much%20higher%20mortgage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20are%20some%20deeply%20entrenched%20features%20of%20the%20American%20mortgage%20system%20that%20make%20it%20unlikely%20we'll%20see%20widespread%20adoption%20of%20Dutch-style%20mortgages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20challenges%20of%20offering%20Dutch-style%20mortgages%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20key%20difference%20between%20American%20and%20many%20foreign%20mortgage%20markets%20is%20that%20in%20the%20US%2C%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20mortgages%20are%20sold%20into%20a%20secondary%20market.%20This%20means%20individual%20mortgages%20are%20bundled%20together%20and%20bought%20and%20sold%20by%20investors.%20This%20may%20sound%20familiar%3A%20The%20buying%20and%20selling%20of%20bundled%20risky%20mortgages%20was%20a%20major%20factor%20in%20the%202008%20housing%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Europe%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20mortgages%20are%20largely%20originated%2C%20held%2C%20and%20serviced%20by%20banks%20or%20portfolio%20lenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDutch-style%20mortgages%20can't%20be%20sold%20into%20the%20secondary%20market%20because%20they%20need%20to%20be%20managed%20by%20an%20individual%20lender%20who%20will%20adjust%20the%20rate%20as%20the%20borrower%20pays%20off%20the%20loan.%20Mortgage-backed%20securities%20investors%20simply%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20see%20a%20decline%20in%20interest%20rates%20for%20the%20underlying%20mortgages%2C%20as%20that%20would%20mean%20a%20lower%20return%20on%20investment.%20This%20would%20make%20it%20tricky%20for%20Dutch-style%20mortgages%20to%20catch%20on%20in%20the%20US%2C%20said%20Guy%20Cecala%2C%20the%20executive%20chairman%20of%20mortgage%20market%20data%20and%20analytics%20firm%20Inside%20Mortgage%20Finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20mortgage%20interest%20rates%20in%20the%20US%20aren't%20determined%20by%20the%20loan-to-value%20ratio%20beyond%20a%20certain%20point.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20borrower%20who%20puts%2050%25%20down%20on%20a%20home%20likely%20won't%20get%20a%20better%20rate%20than%20if%20they%20put%2030%25%20down%2C%20Cecala%20said.%20With%20Dutch-style%20mortgages%2C%20lenders%20%26quot%3Bwould%20have%20to%20be%20convinced%20that%20a%2030%25%20to%2040%25%20equity%20mortgage%20is%20safer%20than%20a%2020%25%20equity%20mortgage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMelissa%20Cohn%2C%20the%20regional%20vice%20president%20at%20the%20lending%20firm%20William%20Raveis%20Mortgage%2C%20cautioned%20that%20the%20true%20benefit%20of%20a%20Dutch-style%20loan%20would%20be%20limited%20to%20people%20who%20plan%20to%20stay%20in%20their%20homes%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20something%20most%20Americans%20don't%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20Americans%20don't%20stay%20in%20their%20homes%20for%2030%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohn%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20average%20home%20ownership%20is%206-9%20years%2C%20and%20people%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20long-term%20benefits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20buyers%20also%20tend%20to%20be%20impatient%20and%20want%20to%20refinance%20their%20home%20loans%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible%2C%20Cecala%20said.%20The%20US%20mortgage%20industry%20is%20built%20around%20this%20behavior%3A%20Refinancings%20make%20up%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.attomdata.com%2Fnews%2Fmarket-trends%2Fmortgage-origination%2Fq4-2023-u-s-home-loan-origination-report%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DRefinance%2520packages%2520comprised%252036.2%2520percent%2Cthe%2520first%2520quarter%2520of%25202021.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%25%20to%2040%25%20of%20all%20mortgage%20originations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20lenders%20would%20likely%20be%20reluctant%20to%20offer%20a%20loan%20that%20automatically%20lowers%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Cecela%20says%20he's%20interested%20to%20see%20what%20happens%20with%20the%20Dutch-style%20mortgages%20newly%20on%20offer%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20catch%20on%20across%20the%20pond%2C%20%26quot%3Bit'll%20cause%20other%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20USA%2C%20to%20take%20a%20look%20at%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falternative-to-high-interest-mortgages-could-be-dutch-style-mortgages-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710337016000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65eb533ace7f1785b2e7f267%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falternative-to-high-interest-mortgages-could-be-dutch-style-mortgages-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dutch-style%20mortgages%20offer%20something%20American%20mortgages%20don't%3A%20automatically%20lower%20interest%20rates%20as%20the%20loan%20is%