rhood%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20nations%20in%20question%20are%20Muslim%20dominated.%20The%20CAA%2C%20passed%20in%202019%2C%20covers%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Christians%2C%20Parsis%2C%20Buddhists%20and%20Jains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20also%20does%20not%20impact%20citizenship%20rules%20of%20India%2C%20sources%20said.%20It%20only%20fast-tracks%20citizenship%20for%20those%20persecuted%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20said%20the%20CAA%20only%20reduces%20the%20waiting%20period%20for%20filing%20an%20application%20for%20citizenship%20to%20qualifying%20individuals%20from%2011%20years%20to%20five.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20does%20not%20discriminate%20against%20Muslims%20from%20those%20nations%20who%20wish%20to%20apply%20for%20Indian%20citizenship.%20%26quot%3BCAA%20does%20not%20cancel%20naturalisation%20laws.%20Therefore%2C%20any%20person%2C%20including%20Muslim%20migrants%20from%20foreign%20countries%2C%20seeking%20to%20be%20an%20Indian%20citizen%2C%20can%20apply%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20also%20said%20Pakistan%20did%20not%20honour%20the%20%26quot%3BNehru-Liaquat%20pact%26quot%3B%E2%80%94a%20treaty%20drawn%20up%20in%201950%20and%20signed%20by%20India's%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20his%20Pakistan%20counterpart%20Liaquat%20Ali%20Khan.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20raised%20this%20matter%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%C2%A0%20unsuccessfully%2C%26quot%3B%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nehru-Liaquat%20pact%20assured%20minorities%20the%20same%20rights%20as%20the%20majority%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20and%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20it%20said%2C%20will%20ensure%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20equality%20of%20citizenship%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religion%2C%20a%20full%20sense%20of%20security%20in%20respect%20of%20life%2C%20culture%2C%20property%20and%20personal%20honour%2C%20freedom%20of%20movement%20within%20each%20country%20and%20freedom%20of%20occupation%2C%20speech%20and%20worship%2C%20subject%20to%20law%20and%20morality%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20would%20participate%20in%20public%20life%2C%20hold%20political%20or%20other%20office%2C%20and%20serve%20in%20their%20country's%20civil%20and%20armed%20forces.%20%26quot%3BBoth%20governments%20declare%20these%20rights%20to%20be%20fundamental%20and%20undertake%20to%20enforce%20them%20effectively%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20treaty.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710332400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fuj9njsbg_caa-rules_625x300_12_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-is-a-parliamentary-recognition-of-neighbourhood-situation-sources-5231281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20discriminate%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20government%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20today%2C%20clarifying%20on%20a%20criticism%20that%20Opposition%20has%20been%20levelling%20since%20the%20draft%20bill%20was%20drawn%20up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-is-a-parliamentary-recognition-of-neighbourhood-situation-sources-5231281%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-is-a-parliamentary-recognition-of-neighbourhood-situation-sources-5231281%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcaa-is-a-parliamentary-recognition-of-neighbourhood-situation-sources-5231281%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20warns%20of%20consequences%20if%20US%20bans%20TikTok%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710332288000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F154BE%2Fproduction%2F_132903278_gettyimages-2079118194.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2F