sts%20with%20names%20of%20candidates%20and%20the%20seats%20they%20were%20chosen%20for%2C%20Trinamool%20hosted%20a%20gala%20event%20in%20Kolkata's%20Brigade%20ground%20last%20weekend%20to%20introduce%20its%20poll%20picks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20led%20the%20parade%2C%20waving%20to%20the%20crowd%20and%20followed%20by%20the%20party's%2042%20candidates%20for%20as%20many%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Bengal.%20Her%20nephew%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20virtually%20the%20No.2%20in%20the%20party%2C%20read%20out%20the%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20surprise%20choice%20walked%20right%20behind%20the%20Trinamool%20chief.%20It%20is%20a%20face%20that%20keeps%20Bengali%20women%20in%20and%20outside%20the%20state%20hooked%20to%20the%20TV%20screen%20for%20an%20hour%20daily.%20It%20was%20the%20face%20of%20Rachna%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2049-year-old%2C%20who%20was%20born%20Jhumjhum%20Banerjee%2C%20first%20made%20headlines%20back%20in%201994%2C%20when%20she%20was%20crowned%20Miss%20Kolkata.%20She%20later%20went%20on%20to%20star%20in%20films%20across%20several%20languages%2C%20including%20Bengali%2C%20Odia%2C%20Telugu%2C%20Tamil%20and%20Kannada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20no%20film%20won%20her%20the%20popularity%20that%20a%20TV%20game%20show%20did.%20'Didi%20No.%201'%20was%20launched%20in%202010%20and%20interestingly%2C%20Rachna%20Banerjee%20was%20not%20its%20first%20anchor.%20She%20took%20over%20in%20the%20second%20season%20and%20then%20the%20producers%20tried%20other%20faces%20too%2C%20but%20none%20stuck%20on%20the%20way%20she%20did.%20The%20show%20has%20a%20bit%20of%20everything%20-%20games%2C%20laughter%20and%20emotions.%20Women%20participants%20narrate%20their%20life%20struggles%2C%20share%20their%20happy%20memories%20and%20the%20anchor%20balances%20fun%20and%20sentimentality.%20The%20result%20is%20the%20longest%20running%20Bengali%20game%20show%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20Trinamool%20announced%20its%20candidates%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20starred%20in%20a%20Didi%20No.%201%20episode.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20few%20people%20had%20thought%20that%20Rachna%20Banerjee%20would%20be%20the%20Trinamool's%20poll%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20celebrity%20candidate%20has%20been%20fielded%20from%20Hooghly%2C%20a%20suburban%20seat%20near%20Kolkata.%20She%20is%20up%20against%20a%20former%20colleague%20and%20actor-turned-politician%2C%20BJP's%20Locket%20Chatterjee.%20Ms%20Chatterjee%20is%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Hooghly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrinamool's%20choice%20of%20Rachna%20Banerjee%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20seen%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20mood%20of%20this%20election.%C2%A0The%20biggest%20political%20talking%20point%20in%20Bengal%20right%20now%20is%20Sandeshkhali.%20An%20island%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%2C%20Sandeshkhali%20has%20made%20headlines%20after%20its%20residents%20accused%20local%20Trinamool%20leaders%20of%20land%20grab%2C%20extortion%20and%20sexual%20harassment.%20While%20Trinamool%20has%20expelled%20its%20local%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20now%20in%20CBI's%20custody%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20mob%20attack%20case%2C%20the%20Oppositon%20BJP%20has%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20its%20efforts%20to%20paint%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20%26quot%3Banti-women%26quot%3B.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20chief%20has%20cultivated%20a%20formidable%20support%20base%20among%20women%20through%20schemes%20like%20Kanyashree%2C%20Rupashree%20and%20Lakshmir%20Bhandar.%20That%20is%20now%20under%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20where%20Rachna%20Banerjee%20comes%20in.%20Yes%2C%20she%20is%20a%20celebrity%2C%20but%20her%20audience%20cuts%20across%20the%20urban-rural%20divide%20and%20spans%20age%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20has%20repeatedly%20propped%20up%20actors%20as%20its%20poll%20picks%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20is%20well%20aware%20that%20the%20glitz%20advantage%20comes%20at%20a%20cost.%20Outgoing%20MPs%20Mimi%20Chakraborty%20and%20Nusrat%20Jahan%20pulled%20off%20stunning%20wins%20in%20the%202019%20election%2C%20but%20the%20party%20had%20to%20tackle%20the%20side-effects%20too.%20Nusrat%20Jahan%2C%20for%20example%2C%20drew%20fire%20for%20posting%20a%20clip%20of%20her%20Valentine's%20Day%20celebrations%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20row.%20This%20prompted%20rivals%20to%20target%20the%20Trinamool%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20propping%20up%20candidates%20not%20invested%20in%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20strategy%20has%20paid%20off%20for%20Ms%20Banerjee%20so%20far.%20Hence%2C%20the%20former%20celebrity%20picks%20have%20made%20way%20for%20new%20ones.%20But%20with%20Rachana%20Banerjee%2C%20Trinamool%20is%20looking%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20a%20far%20wider%20demographic%20than%20it%20has%20earlier%20done.%20Unlike%20Mimi%20Chakraborty%2C%20Nusrat%20Jahan%20or%20actor%20Dev%20-%20who%20has%20been%20repeated%20as%20a%20candidate%20this%20time%20-%20Rachna%20comes%20on%20TV%20daily.%20Her%20audience%20spans%20across%20economic%20classes%20and%20both%20urban%20and%20rural%20belts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20a%20sea%20of%20difference%20between%20a%20TV%20studio%20and%20the%20poll%20arena.%20Rachana%20Banerjee%20knows%20there%20are%20no%20retakes%20here.%20In%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20she%20has%20said%20the%20shooting%20of%20Didi%20No%201%20may%20face%20disruptions%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20months.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20be%20campaigning%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20But%20I%20will%20come%20and%20shoot%20at%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20Then%20came%20the%20big%20question%3A%20why%20politics%3F%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20need%20power%20and%20a%20platform%20to%20work%20for%20people%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20bigger%20platform%20than%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710331020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1pt3bnno_rachna-banerjee-mamata-banerjee_625x300_13_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsandeshkhali-mamata-banerjee-rachna-banerjee-didi-bets-on-didi-no-1-star-to-woo-women-voters-amid-sandeshkhali-row-5231370%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20there%20was%20an%20award%20for%20glitz%20quotient%20in%20announcing%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20candidates%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20would%20be%20a%20clear%20winner.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsandeshkhali-mamata-banerjee-rachna-banerjee-didi-bets-on-didi-no-1-star-to-woo-women-voters-amid-sandeshkhali-row-5231370%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Details%20on%20electoral%20bonds%20will%20be%20disclosed%20on%20time%3A%20CEC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710330614000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108466772%2Cimgsize-19206.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fdetails-on-electoral-bonds-will-be-disclosed-on-time-chief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar%2Farticleshow%2F108466522.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fdetails-on-electoral-bonds-will-be-disclosed-on-time-chief-election-commissioner-rajiv-kumar%2Farticleshow%2F108466522.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Celebs%20who%20married%20their%20childhood%20sweethearts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710330594000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108466750%2Cimgsize-66144.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffrom-anant-ambani-to-varun-dhawan-celebs-show-us-the-power-of-first-love-with-childhood-sweethearts%2Farticleshow%2F108466514.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108466514.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBollywood's%20enduring%20celebrity%20couples%20like%20Anant%20Ambani%20and%20Radhika%20Merchant%2C%20Varun%20Dhawan%20and%20Natasha%20Dalal%2C%20Zayed%20Khan%20and%20Malaika%20Parekh%2C%20Ayushmann%20Khurrana%20and%20Tahira%20Kashyap%2C%20Fardeen%20Khan%20and%20Natasha%20Madhvani%2C%20inspire%20fans%20with%20their%20love%20stories%20and%20commitment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ffrom-anant-ambani-to-varun-dhawan-celebs-show-us-the-power-of-first-love-with-childhood-sweethearts%2Farticleshow%2F108466514.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shreyas%20Iyer%20Stars%20For%20Mumbai%20After%20Much%20Criticism.%20KKR%20Coach%20Says%20This%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20head%20coach%20Chandrakant%20Pandit%20was%20all%20praise%20for%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20star%20batter%20scored%2095%20for%20Mumbai%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20of%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20final%20against%20Vidarbha.%20Iyer%2C%20who%20dismissed%20for%20just%20seven%20in%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20smashed%2010%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes%20during%20his%20whirlwind%20knock.%20Pandit%2C%20who%20will%20join%20hands%20with%20Iyer%20during%20IPL%202024%2C%20hailed%20the%20KKR%20skipper%20for%20his%20fearlessness%20and%20compared%20his%20knock%20to%20the%20World%20Cup%20semi-final%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20an%20important%20innings%20for%20Shreyas%20and%20he%20delivered%20it%20when%20it%20mattered.%20Although%20in%20a%20different%20format%2C%20his%20innings%20resembled%20the%20one%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20semifinal%20here%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20against%20New%20Zealand%20(he%20had%20scored%20105%20off%2070%20deliveries%20then).%20He%20is%20playing%20good%20cricket%20and%20it%20was%20bad%20luck%20that%20he%20could%20not%20score%20big%20runs%20in%20the%20last%20few%20games%2C%26quot%3B%20Pandit%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cricbuzz.com%2Fcricket-news%2F129843%2Franji-trophy-2023-24-final-chandrakant-pandit-hails-shreyas-iyers-fearless-performance-mumbai-vs-vidarbha%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20he%20smashed%2010%20boundaries%20and%20three%20sixes%20is%20an%20indication%20that%20he%20is%20playing%20fearlessly%20and%20is%20not%20changing%20his%20style%20of%20play.%20The%20innings%20will%20stand%20him%20in%20good%20stead%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20unversed%2C%20Iyer%20had%20smashed%20105%20off%20just%2070%20balls%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20semi-final%20against%20New%20Zealand%2C%20also%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20final%2C%20Iyer%20will%20associate%20with%20Chandrakant%20Pandit%20at%20KKR%2C%20having%20missed%20the%20last%20season%20of%20IPL%20due%20to%20an%20injury.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandit%20also%20hailed%20Mumbai%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ajinkya%20Rahane%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F965-ajinkya-rahane-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAjinkya%20Rahane%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20his%20knock%20in%20the%20second%20innings%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20veteran%20played%20the%20best%20knock%20for%20his%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20liked%20his%20(Musheer)%20approach%20and%20his%20partnership%20with%20Iyer%20may%20have%20made%20things%20difficult%20for%20Vidrabha.%20But%20the%20best%20knock%20I%20think%20came%20from%20Ajinkya%20(73).%20He%20scored%20those%20runs%20when%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Umesh%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1258-umesh-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3EUmesh%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20good%20spell.%20Now%20with%20so%20many%20runs%20on%20the%20board%2C%20it%20will%20be%20very%20difficult%20for%20Vidarbha%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710330420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fjeuu17k8_shreyas-iyer-pti_625x300_13_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdelivered-when-it-mattered-kkr-coach-on-fearless-shreyas-iyer-after-ranji-heroics-5229284%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shreyas%20Iyer%20scored%2095%20for%20Mumbai%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20of%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20final%20against%20Vidarbha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Short%20On%20Names%20For%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%2C%20BJP%20And%20KCR%20Party%20Fight%20Over%20Candidate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20in%20Telangana%20today%20fought%20over%20a%20former%20MLA%20who%20had%20announced%20he%20would%20join%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20BRS%20MLA%20Aroori%20Ramesh%20was%20at%20home%20when%20BRS%20leaders%20barged%20in%20and%20allegedly%20tried%20to%20take%20him%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20Ramesh%20yesterday%20met%20Telangana%20BJP%20chief%20G%20Kishan%20Reddy%2C%20the%20former%20BRS%20leader%20announced%20he%20would%20join%20the%20BJP%20this%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20press%20conference%20to%20announce%20his%20resignation%20from%20the%20BRS%2C%20former%20state%20minister%20Errabelli%20Dayakar%20and%20others%20barged%20in%20and%20allegedly%20tried%20to%20convince%20Mr%20Ramesh%20not%20to%20join%20the%20BJP.%20They%20reportedly%20made%20him%20speak%20to%20BRS%20leader%20Harish%20Rao%20on%20phone%2C%20after%20which%20they%20allegedly%20forced%20Mr%20Ramesh%20into%20a%20car%20to%20take%20him%20to%20Hyderabad%2C%20where%20senior%20BRS%20leaders%20including%20Mr%20Rao%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20would%20be%20waiting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20BRS%20and%20BJP%20supporters%20clashed%20outside%20Mr%20Ramesh's%20house%20when%20word%20spread%20he%20had%20been%20allegedly%20'kidnapped'%20by%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20visuals%2C%20Mr%20Ramesh%20is%20seen%20being%20pulled%20out%20of%20a%20car%20in%20which%20Errabelli%20Dayakar%20is%20sitting%20in%20the%20front%20seat.%20The%20car%20was%20reportedly%20intercepted%20by%20BJP%20supporters%20and%20stopped%20from%20going%20towards%20to%20Hyderabad.%20The%20BJP%20supporters%20dialled%20the%20state%20BJP%20chief%20and%20made%20Mr%20Ramesh%20speak%20to%20him%20in%20front%20of%20cameras%3B%20he%20is%20heard%20saying%20he%20would%20tell%20the%20BRS%20leadership%20he%20has%20quit.%20Visuals%20showed%20the%20former%20MLAs%20shirt%20had%20been%20torn%20in%20the%20scuffle.%20He%20looked%20hassled%20and%20confused%20about%20what%20was%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20has%20been%20struggling%20to%20find%20candidates%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20party%20has%20lost%20three%20MPs%20in%20recent%20times%20-%20one%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20two%20to%20the%20BJP.%20Ranjith%20Reddy%20from%20Chevella%20has%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20he%20does%20not%20want%20to%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20reportedly%20wanted%20to%20field%20Mr%20Ramesh%20from%20Warangal%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20had%20made%20the%20same%20offer%2C%20and%20he%20preferred%20the%20party%20that%20is%20ruling%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ramesh%20told%20reporters%20he%20was%20humiliated%20in%20the%20BRS%20despite%20winning%20with%20a%20good%20majority%20in%20the%20past%20and%20wanted%20to%20move%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20too%2C%20does%20not%20have%20enough%20candidates%20with%20potential%20to%20win%20and%20so%20is%20looking%20to%20induct%20leaders%20from%20other%20parties%20such%20as%20the%20BRS%2C%20which%20is%20now%20on%20the%20back%20foot%20after%20its%20defeat%20in%20the%20last%20assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20BRS%20MP%20BB%20Patil%20from%20Zaheerabad%20a%20day%20after%20he%20joined%20the%20party%2C%20even%20though%20the%20BRS%20had%20wanted%20to%20make%20him%20contest%20from%20the%20same%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20made%20Bharat%20Prasad%20its%20candidate%20from%20Nagarkurnool%20(Scheduled%20Castes%20reserved)%20constituency%20just%20two%20days%20after%20his%20father%20and%20MP%20P%20Ramulu%20resigned%20from%20the%20BRS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBRS%20leader%20B%20Vinod%20Kumar%2C%20who%20has%20been%20fielded%20by%20the%20party%20from%20Karimnagar%2C%20said%20five%20out%20of%20the%20nine%20candidates%20announced%20by%20the%20BJP%20are%20from%20the%20BRS%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20former%20BRS%20MPs%20Ajmeera%20Sitaram%20Naik%20(Mahbubabad)%20and%20Godam%20Nagesh%20(Adilabad)%2C%20and%20two%20former%20MLAs%20Jalagam%20Venkat%20Rao%20(Kothagudem)%20and%20S%20Saidi%20Reddy%20(Huzurnagar)%2C%20have%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20BRS%20leader%2C%20G%20Srinivas%2C%20who%20unsuccessfully%20contested%20from%20Peddapalli%2C%20has%20also%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710330360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fc25v2qag_aroori-ramesh_625x300_13_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftelangana-news%2Fshort-on-names-for-lok-sabha-polls-bjp-and-kcrs-party-fight-over-candidate-aroori-ramesh-in-telangana-5231296%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20in%20Telangana%20today%20fought%20over%20a%20former%