4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fyuvraj-singh-trolls-shubman-gill-in-rohit-sharmas-garden-mein-ghoomne-post%2Farticleshow%2F108465748.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%20High%20Court%20Asks%20Government%20to%20Respond%20on%20'Rs%2025%2C000-Crore%20Land%20Scam'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F29143159%2FHigh_Court_of_AP.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHyderabad%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Telangana%20high%20court%20on%20Tuesday%20(March%2012)%20directed%20the%20petitioners%20in%20a%20writ%20petition%20relating%20to%20huge%20alleged%20land%20scam%20to%20take%20out%20personal%20notices%20to%20the%20respondents%2C%20including%20official%20respondents.%20During%20the%20recently%20concluded%20assembly%20elections%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frahul-gandhi-digitised-land-records-telangana%5C%22%3Ereported%20on%20allegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20a%20land%20scam%20in%20the%20making%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20Dharani%20Act%2C%20the%20controversial%20land%20records%20management%20system%20devised%20by%20the%20erstwhile%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20writ%20petition%2C%20petitioners%20highlighted%20the%2040-years%20saga%20of%20alleged%20cheating%20and%20creating%20fraudulent%20sale%20transactions%20amounting%20to%20about%20Rs%2025%2C000-crore%20scam%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20capital%20city%2C%20Hyderabad.%20The%20contention%20of%20the%20petitioners%20is%20that%20they%20purchased%20the%20plots%20between%201983%20and%201986%20from%20the%20then%20%3Cem%3Epattedars%3C%2Fem%3E%20through%20their%20authorised%20general%20power%20of%20attorney.%20However%2C%20concealing%20this%20fact%2C%20the%20pattedars%20obtained%20%E2%80%98patta%20passbooks%E2%80%99%20(land%20title%20deeds)%20usually%20issued%20by%20the%20state%20government%20to%20the%20farmers%2Fland%20owners.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20erstwhile%20land%20owners%20created%20close%20to%201%2C000%20sham%20sale%20deeds%20in%20spite%20of%20repeated%20directions%20from%20various%20courts%20and%20revenue%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plot%20owners%E2%80%99%20association%20also%20filed%20a%20petition%20to%20the%20then%20Ranga%20Reddy%20district%20revenue%20court%20requesting%20it%20to%20cancel%20the%20illegally%20issued%20pattadar%20passbooks.%20After%20the%20enquiry%20and%20hearing%2C%20the%20joint%20collector%E2%80%99s%20court%20categorically%20asked%20the%20revenue%20authorities%20to%20cancel%20the%20pattadar%20passbooks%20as%20the%20said%20land%20in%20question%20was%20converted%20into%20plots%20and%20sold%20to%20more%20than%203%2C000%20people.%20But%20it%20turned%20out%20that%20the%20revenue%20authorities%20paid%20scant%20respect%20to%20the%20joint%20collector%E2%80%99s%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20state%20government%20brought%20the%20Dharani%20Act%2C%20the%20petitioners%20filed%20a%20writ%20petition%20seeking%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20asking%20revenue%20authorities%20to%20exclude%20certain%20survey%20numbers%20of%20Vattinagulapally%20village%20of%20Ranga%20Reddy%20district%20from%20the%20Dharani%20portal%20to%20restrict%20the%20further%20creation%20of%20fraudulent%20transactions.%20The%20high%20court%20restrained%20the%20revenue%20authorities%20from%20entertaining%20any%20sale%20transactions.%20Despite%20this%2C%20the%20revenue%20authorities%20allegedly%20registered%20close%20to%20200%20sale%20deeds%20between%20July%202022%20and%20March%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202023%2C%20the%20high%20court%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20C.V.%20Bhaskar%20Reddy%20directed%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20Cyberabad%20and%20other%20officials%20not%20to%20take%20any%20action%20on%20plot%20owners.%20But%20despite%20high%20court%20directions%2C%20police%20officials%20from%20Ganchibowli%20Police%20Station%20were%20obstructing%20the%20plot%20owners%20from%20entering%20their%20plots.%20They%20are%20also%20alleged%20to%20have%20taken%20away%20land%20survey%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%2C%20as%20an%20unusual%20method%20of%20protest%2C%20filed%20nominations%20against%20KCR%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20assembly%20elections%20to%20draw%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20government%20to%20their%20plight.%20KCR%20is%20said%20to%20have%20directed%20his%20lieutenant%20Harish%20Rao%20to%20convince%20the%20plot%20owners%20to%20withdraw%20nominations.%20After%20assurances%20given%20by%20Hari%20Rao%2C%20the%20petitioners%20withdrew%20their%20nominations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20as%20there%20is%20no%20change%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20hundreds%20of%20plot%20owners%20have%20submitted%20a%20representation%20to%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%2C%20Telangana%20to%20take%20action%20against%20the%20%E2%80%98land%20mafia%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Crime%20Investigation%20Department%20was%20entrusted%20with%20the%20job%20of%20enquiry%20and%20preparing%20a%20dossier%20on%20the%20issue.%20The%20petitioners%20drew%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20high%20court%20to%20the%20CID%20report%20and%20pleaded%20for%20it%20to%20direct%20the%20police%20department%20to%20register%20criminal%20cases%20and%20conduct%20an%20enquiry%20by%20appointing%20a%20Special%20Investigating%20Team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20on%20Tuesday%20directed%20the%20state%20government%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20allegations.%20The%20case%20is%20set%20to%20be%20heard%20on%20April%2015.%20Advocates%20Nallamasu%20Krishna%20and%20Veeraiah%20Konduri%20represented%20the%20petitioners.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710329438000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F29143159%2FHigh_Court_of_AP.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthew