dnesday%20and%20went%20below%20the%2073%2C000%20level%20before%20making%20some%20recovery%20while%20the%20Nifty%20slid%20by%20over%201%25.%20The%20smallcap%20and%20midcap%20indices%20fell%20the%20most%2C%20with%20the%20BSE%20smallcap%20index%20going%20down%20by%20over%205%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Sensex%20closed%20906%20points%20down%20to%20settle%20at%2072%2C761%2C%20the%20Nifty%20was%20down%20338%20points%20and%20closed%20three%20points%20short%20of%2022%2C000.%20Over%2013%20lakh%20crore%20of%20investor%20wealth%20was%20wiped%20out%20in%20the%20day's%20trading%20session.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20have%20attributed%20the%20fall%2C%20which%20is%20coming%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20S%26amp%3BP500%20had%20hit%20a%20record%20high%2C%20to%20liquidity%20overflowing%20and%20valuations%20in%20the%20smallcap%20and%20midcap%20indices%20being%20stretched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarket%20expert%20Ambareesh%20Baliga%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20valuations%20were%20expensive%20and%20the%20stocks%20continued%20to%20move%20up%20because%20of%20liquidity.%20People%20were%20making%20money%20so%20they%20were%20putting%20in%20more%20funds%2C%20because%20of%20which%20the%20stocks%20were%20going%20up.%20It%20was%20not%20because%20of%20valuation.%20But%20now%2C%20In%20the%20past%20week%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20that%20the%20regulators%20are%20worried%20about%20the%20valuations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20percolated%20down%20even%20to%20the%20mutual%20funds%2C%20who%20have%20started%20restricting%20fund%20flow%20into%20the%20small%20and%20midcap%20funds.%20I%20think%20that%20is%20what%20is%20playing%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Baliga%20said%20there%20has%20been%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20correction%2C%20like%20the%205%25%20drop%20in%20the%20smallcap%20index.%20This%2C%20he%20said%2C%20points%20to%20some%20of%20the%20smallcap%20stocks%20correcting%20between%2020%20and%2040%25%20in%20some%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20that%20has%20created%20some%20amount%20of%20panic%20among%20those%20who%20had%20seen%20only%20profits%20till%20date%20in%20the%20past%20so%20many%20months.%20I%20think%20the%20first%20sign%20of%20huge%20losses%20has%20started%20causing%20panic.%20And%20when%20you%20have%20this%20panic%2C%20you%20stop%20investing%20further.%20So%20the%20liquidity%2C%20which%20was%20driving%20up%20the%20stocks%2C%20has%20started%20drying%20up.%20I%20think%20this%20could%20be%20just%20the%20beginning%2C%20we%20could%20see%20some%20more%20correction%20from%20here%20as%20the%20liquidity%20dries%20up%20further%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expert%20said%20retail%20investors%20should%20book%20their%20profits%20or%20losses%20and%20start%20moving%20into%20large-cap%20stocks%2C%20because%20they%20are%20more%20stable%20and%20the%20valuations%20are%20still%20not%20expensive.%20%26quot%3BDo%20not%20invest%20based%20on%20tips%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710328980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fl8lra8j_bse-generic-share-market-generic-sensex-generic-pti_625x300_21_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fsensex-nifty-markets-crash-smallcap-index-sensex-tumbles-over-900-points-nifty-down-338-as-markets-see-correction-5230854%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Sensex%20crashed%20nearly%201%2C000%20points%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20went%20below%20the%2073%2C000%20level%20before%20making%20some%20recovery%20while%20the%20Nifty%20slid%20by%20over%201%25.%20The%20smallcap%20and%20midcap%20indices%20fell%20the%20most%2C%20with%20the%20BSE%20smallcap%20index%20going%20down%20by%20over%205%25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fsensex-nifty-markets-crash-smallcap-index-sensex-tumbles-over-900-points-nifty-down-338-as-markets-see-correction-5230854%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22