m%20just%20finished%20a%204-1%20rout%20of%20England%20in%20a%20five-Test%20series.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20marshalled%20a%20young%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20with%20absolute%20control%20as%20the%20side%20consolidated%20its%20place%20on%20top%20of%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20standings.%20The%20loss%20was%20a%20first%20for%20the%20Bazaball%20era%20in%20England%20Test%20cricket.%20There%20was%20much%20hype%20surrounding%20England's%20aggressive%20brand%20of%20Test%20cricket%20under%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Brendon%20McCullum%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F290-brendon-mccullum-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBrendon%20McCullum%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ben%20Stokes%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1434-ben-stokes-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBen%20Stokes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20won%20the%20first%20Test%20too%20but%20later%20could%20not%20stop%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20commented%20on%20the%20sledging%20Incidents%20between%20the%20two%20teams%20during%20the%20series.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20also%20the%20reason%20why%20the%20England%20and%20Indian%20players%20get%20into%20verbal%20skirmishes%20so%20often%20when%20they%20are%20playing%20against%20each%20other.%20Not%20a%20lot%20of%20England%20players%20are%20picked%20in%20the%20IPL%2C%20mainly%20because%20they%20can%20be%20withdrawn%20by%20their%20Board%20anytime%20for%20a%20preparation%20camp%20or%20something%2C%20which%20leaves%20the%20franchises%20in%20a%20lurch%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20wrote%20in%20a%20column%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsportstar.thehindu.com%2Fcricket%2Franji-trophy-match-fees-doubled-india-test-cricket-fees-bcci-ind-eng%2Farticle67942378.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESportstar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20them%20can't%20stomach%20the%20fees%20for%20which%20some%20of%20the%20Indian%20players%20are%20bought%20and%20compare%20their%20achievements%20at%20the%20international%20level%20when%20the%20IPL%20auction%20dynamics%20can%20be%20so%20volatile%20and%20hard%20to%20explain%20or%20even%20understand.%20So%20you%20see%20more%20lip%20in%20the%20India-England%20encounters%20than%20in%20any%20other%20India%20match.%20That's%20why%20the%20pleasure%20of%20beating%20England%20is%20always%20greater.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%20also%20gave%20his%20take%20on%20England's%20Bazball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Ben%20Stokes'%20team%20came%20to%20India%2C%20there%20was%20a%20buzz%20around%20it%20as%20they%20had%20started%20to%20play%20a%20brand%20of%20aggressive%20batting%20that%20the%20British%20media%20dubbed%20'Bazball'.%20This%20was%20because%20the%20new%20coach%20Brendon%20McCullum's%20nickname%20is%20'Baz'.%20He%20encouraged%20the%20players%20to%20always%20go%20in%20with%20a%20positive%20mindset%20and%20to%20keep%20at%20it%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20result.%20The%20batting%20thus%20became%20ultra-aggressive%2C%20with%20players%20encouraged%20to%20hit%20sixes%20and%20fours%20with%20a%20dot%20ball%20as%20the%20least%20preferred%20option.%20Stokes%20wanted%20his%20players%20to%20play%20like%20rock%20stars%2C%20whatever%20that%20means%2C%20and%20with%20England%20beginning%20to%20win%20games%2C%20the%20fans%20and%20the%20media%20were%20euphoric%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20batting%20was%20exciting%20to%20watch%20with%20the%20way%20the%20scoreboard%20rattled%20along.%20They%20even%20scored%20more%20than%20500%20runs%20in%20a%20day%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20then%20went%20on%20to%20win%20all%20the%20Test%20matches%20played%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20all%20this%20batting%20frenzy%20was%20on%20good%20batting%20pitches%20against%20opposition%20attacks%20that%20weren't%20quite%20threatening.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710328740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F292u57lc_suni-gavaskar_625x300_12_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fengland-stars-cant-stomach-indian-players-fees-sunil-gavaskars-no-holds-barred-bashing-on-skirmishes-5231099%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20marshalled%20a%20young%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20with%20absolute%20control%20against%20England%20as%20the%20side%20consolidated%20its%20place%20on%20top%20of%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20standings%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Navel%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Motherhood%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Heirloom%E2%80%99%20Share%20Honors%20at%20Evenly%20Spread%20HAF%20Project%20Market%20Awards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710328638000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FHAF-Award-winners-2024.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235940479%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20honors%20were%20evenly%20distributed%20at%20the%202024%20Hong%20Kong%20%E2%80%93%20Asia%20Film%20Financing%20Forum%20awards%20with%20no%20film%20project%20winning%20more%20than%20two%20prizes.%20Zhang%20Zhongchen%E2%80%99s%20work-in-progress%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Land%20is%20Our%20Navel%E2%80%9D%20(China)%2C%20that%20tracks%20a%20surreal%20journey%20beginning%20in%20a%20village%2C%20will%20be%20one%20of%20five%20projects%20invited%20to%20go%20to%20Cannes.%20It%