20wild%20after%20I%20got%20my%20first%20camera%20was%20of%20a%20Himalayan%20Brown%20Bear%20in%20a%20village%20called%20Huliya%20near%20Drass.%20The%20photo%20was%20of%20a%20mother%20and%20her%20cub%20playing%20in%20the%20snow.%20Witnessing%20these%20majestic%20creatures%20in%20their%20natural%20habitat%20was%20a%20very%20captivating%20experience%2C%20and%20I%20was%20thrilled%20to%20seize%20the%20opportunity%20to%20document%20that%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Karamjeet%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisit%20Karamjeet%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcaramjeet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Instagram%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20spell-binding%20photographs%20of%20the%20wildlife%20in%20Ladakh.%C2%A0%20In%20his%20photos%2C%20he%20has%20managed%20to%20capture%20a%20variety%20of%20endangered%20species%20ranging%20from%20the%20elusive%20snow%20leopard%20(%3Cem%3EPanthera%20uncia%3C%2Fem%3E)%20to%20the%20solitary%20Himalayan%20Brown%20Bear%20(%3Cem%3EUrsus%20arctos%20isabellinus%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20Pallas%E2%80%99s%20Cat%20(%3Cem%3EOtocolobus%20manul%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20Tibetan%20Wolf%20(%3Cem%3ECanis%20lupus%20chanco%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20the%20Urial%20(%3Cem%3EOvis%20orientalis)%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20Eurasian%20eagle%20owl%20(%3Cem%3EBubo%20bubo%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20bearded%20vulture%20(%3Cem%3EGypaetus%20barbatus)%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20among%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20beyond%20wildlife%2C%20Karamjeet%20has%20also%20captured%20spectacular%20photos%20of%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20landscape%2C%20its%20tribes%20and%20night%20skies.%20As%20Karamjeet%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CLadakh%20contains%20an%20amazing%20range%20of%20wildlife%2C%20including%20birds%20and%20mammals.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20shame%20not%20many%20people%20notice%20these%20incredible%20creatures.%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%20awest